2703 is_icall = TRUE;
2704 goto sub_common;
2705 case I_REDUCE_PARITY:
2706 rtlRtn = RTE_global_parity;
2707 is_icall = TRUE;
2708 goto sub_common;
2709 case I_REDUCE_IANY:
2710 rtlRtn = RTE_global_iany;
2711 is_icall = TRUE;
2712 goto sub_common;
2713 case I_REDUCE_IALL:
2714 rtlRtn = RTE_global_iall;
2715 is_icall = TRUE;
2716 goto sub_common;
2717 case I_REDUCE_IPARITY:
2718 rtlRtn = RTE_global_iparity;
2719 is_icall = TRUE;
2720 goto sub_common;
2721 case I_REDUCE_MINVAL:
2722 rtlRtn = RTE_global_minval;
2723 is_icall = TRUE;
2724 goto sub_common;
2725 case I_REDUCE_MAXVAL:
2726 rtlRtn = RTE_global_maxval;
2727 is_icall = TRUE;
2728 goto sub_common;
2729 case I_REDUCE_FIRSTMAX:
2730 rtlRtn = RTE_global_firstmax;
2731 is_icall = FALSE;
2732 /*********************************************
2733 ====================================
2734 POSSIBLY NEED THIS SINCE is_icall = FALSE...
2735 THIS IS OFTEN IN OTHER SUCH CASES. IN THIS CASE, NEED TO OVER-RIDE WHAT'S
2736 DONE IN sub_common).
2737 *BUT*, NOT DONE FOR _SECNDS, I_TIME, I_IDATE OR I_LASTVAL (THE LAST OF
2738 WHICH LOOKS JUST LIKE REDUCE_MAXVAL.)
2739 HENCE, TRY WITHOUT THE FOLLOWING TO START WITH!
2740 ====================================
2741 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
2742 for (i = 0; i < nargs; ++i) {
2743 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = ARGT_ARG(func_args, i);
2744 }
2745 *********************************************/
2746 goto sub_common;
2747 case I_REDUCE_FIRSTMIN:
2748 rtlRtn = RTE_global_firstmin;
2749 is_icall = FALSE;
2750 goto sub_common;
2751 case I_REDUCE_LASTMAX:
2752 rtlRtn = RTE_global_lastmax;
2753 is_icall = FALSE;
2754 goto sub_common;
2755 case I_REDUCE_LASTMIN:
2756 rtlRtn = RTE_global_lastmin;
2757 is_icall = FALSE;
2758 goto sub_common;
2759 sub_common:
2760 nargs = ARGT_CNT(func_args);
2761 newargt = func_args;
2762 newsym = sym_mkfunc(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn), DT_NONE);
2763 retval = 0;
2764 goto ret_call;
2765 case I_PTR2_ASSIGN:
2766 check_pointer_type(ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0), ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1),
2767 arg_gbl.std, 0);
2768 if (!XBIT(58, 0x22)) {
2769 /* ...no changes unless caller remapping. */
2770 return -1;
2771 }
2772 ast = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
2773 if (A_TYPEG(ast) != A_ID || STYPEG(A_SPTRG(ast)) != ST_ARRAY ||
2774 POINTERG(A_SPTRG(ast))) {
2775 /* ...no changes unless pointer assigned to whole array. */
2776 return -1;
2777 }
2778 /* Create call:
2779 * pghpf_ptr_asgn[_char](ptr_base, ptr_desc, arr_base, arr_desc, vlb),
2780 * where vlb is a vector of lower bounds of arr_base. */
2781 sptr = A_SPTRG(ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0));
2782 nargs = 5;
2783 if (XBIT(70, 0x20)) {
2784 if (MIDNUMG(sptr))
2785 ++nargs;
2786 if (PTROFFG(sptr))
2787 ++nargs;
2788 }
2789 rtlRtn = DTYG(A_DTYPEG(ast)) == TY_CHAR ? RTE_ptr_asgn_chara : RTE_ptr_asgn;
2790 newsym = sym_mkfunc_nodesc(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn), dtype);
2791 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
2792 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
2793 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = mk_id(DESCRG(sptr));
2794 DESCUSEDP(sptr, TRUE);
2795 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 2) = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
2796 temp_sptr = A_SPTRG(ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1));
2797 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 3) = mk_id(DESCRG(temp_sptr));
2798 DESCUSEDP(temp_sptr, TRUE);
2799 temp_arr = sym_get_array(SYMNAME(temp_sptr), "v", DT_INT, 1);
2800 NODESCP(temp_arr, TRUE);
2801 ALLOCP(temp_arr, FALSE);
2802 dtype = DTYPEG(temp_arr);
2803 ADD_NOBOUNDS(dtype) = 0;
2804 ADD_MLPYR(dtype, 0) = astb.i1;
2805 ADD_LWAST(dtype, 0) = ADD_LWBD(dtype, 0) = astb.i1;
2806 ndims = rank_of_sym(temp_sptr);
2807 ADD_UPAST(dtype, 0) = ADD_UPBD(dtype, 0) = mk_cval(ndims, DT_INT);
2808 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 4) = mk_id(temp_arr);
2809 nargs = 5;
2810 if (XBIT(70, 0x20)) {
2811 /* add pointer, offset to argument list */
2812 if (MIDNUMG(sptr)) {
2813 ARGT_ARG(newargt, nargs) = mk_id(MIDNUMG(sptr));
2814 ++nargs;
2815 }
2816 if (PTROFFG(sptr)) {
2817 ARGT_ARG(newargt, nargs) = mk_id(PTROFFG(sptr));
2818 ++nargs;
2819 }
2820 }
2821 dtype = DTYPEG(temp_sptr);
2822 for (dim = 0; dim < ndims; dim++) {
2823 subscr[0] = mk_cval(dim + 1, DT_INT);
2824 ast = mk_subscr(mk_id(temp_arr), subscr, 1, DT_INT);
2825 ast = mk_assn_stmt(ast, ADD_LWAST(dtype, dim), DT_INT);
2826 add_stmt_before(ast, arg_gbl.std);
2827 }
2828 if (XBIT(49, 0x8000)) {
2829 /* ...no Cray pointers. */
2830 /* Set the offset to 1 because every destination pointer P will
2831 * be transformed later to P(offset). */
2832 temp_sptr = A_SPTRG(ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0));
2833 temp_sptr = PTROFFG(temp_sptr);
2834 assert(temp_sptr, "rewrite_func_ast: no pointer offset", func_ast, 3);
2835 ast = mk_assn_stmt(mk_id(temp_sptr), astb.i1, DT_INT);
2836 add_stmt_before(ast, arg_gbl.std);
2837 }
2838 is_icall = FALSE;
2839 goto ret_call;
2840 case I_GETARG:
2841 case I_GET_COMMAND:
2842 case I_GET_COMMAND_ARGUMENT:
2843 if (optype == I_GETARG) {
2844 rtlRtn = RTE_getarga;
2845 nargs = 3;
2846 } else if (optype == I_GET_COMMAND) {
2847 rtlRtn = RTE_get_cmda;
2848 nargs = 4;
2849 } else {
2850 rtlRtn = RTE_get_cmd_arga;
2851 nargs = 5;
2852 }
2853 newsym = sym_mkfunc_nodesc(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn), DT_INT);
2854 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
2855 for (i = 0; i < nargs - 1; i++) {
2856 int arg = ARGT_ARG(func_args, i);
2857 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg != 0 ? arg : i == 0 ? astb.ptr0c : astb.ptr0;
2858 }
2859 ARGT_ARG(newargt, nargs - 1) =
2860 mk_cval(size_of(stb.user.dt_int), astb.bnd.dtype);
2861 is_icall = FALSE;
2862 goto ret_call;
2863 case I_GET_ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLE:
2864 newsym = sym_mkfunc_nodesc(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_get_env_vara), DT_INT);
2865 nargs = 6;
2866 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
2867 for (i = 0; i < nargs - 1; i++) {
2868 int arg = ARGT_ARG(func_args, i);
2869 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg != 0 ? arg : i == 1 ? astb.ptr0c : astb.ptr0;
2870 }
2871 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 5) = mk_cval(size_of(stb.user.dt_int), DT_INT4);
2872 is_icall = FALSE;
2873 goto ret_call;
2874 default:
2875 goto ret_norm;
2876 }
2877
2878ret_new:
2879 /* get the name of the library routine */
2880 newsym = sym_mkfunc(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn), DT_NONE);
2881 /* get the temp and add the necessary statements */
2882 if (shape != 0) {
2883 /* need to put this into a temp */
2884 temp_arr = mk_result_sptr(func_ast, func_args, subscr, DTY(dtype + 1), lhs,
2885 &retval);
2886 if (temp_arr != 0) {
2887 /* add temp_arr as argument */
2888 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = retval;
2889 if (ALLOCG(temp_arr)) {
2890 mk_mem_allocate(mk_id(temp_arr), subscr, arg_gbl.std, ast_from_len);
2891 mk_mem_deallocate(mk_id(temp_arr), arg_gbl.std);
2892 }
2893 } else {
2894 /* lhs was distributed properly for this intr */
2895 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = lhs;
2896 retval = 0;
2897 }
2898 } else {
2899 /* need to put this into a scalar temp */
2900 int temp_sclr = sym_get_scalar("tmp", "r", dtype);
2901 /* add temp_sclr as argument */
2902 retval = mk_id(temp_sclr);
2903 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = retval;
2904 }
2905
2906ret_call:
2907 /* add call to function */
2908 /* make every call ICALL iff call changes the first argument and
2909 no side effect, this will help optimizer */
2910 ast =
2911 mk_func_node(is_icall ? A_ICALL : A_CALL, mk_id(newsym), nargs, newargt);
2912 A_OPTYPEP(ast, optype);
2913 add_stmt_before(ast, arg_gbl.std);
2914 return retval;
2915
2916ret_norm:
2917 retval = mk_func_node(type, A_LOPG(func_ast), A_ARGCNTG(func_ast), func_args);
2918 if (A_SRCG(func_ast)) { /* type bound procedure pass_arg%member part */
2919 A_SRCP(retval, A_SRCG(func_ast));
2920 }
2921 A_DTYPEP(retval, dtype);
2922 A_SHAPEP(retval, shape);
2923 A_OPTYPEP(retval, optype);
2924
2925 if (shape == 0 && take_out_user_def_func(func_ast)) {
2926 int temp_ast, temp_sptr;
2927 if (arg_gbl.lhs == 0) {
2928 int func = procsym_of_ast(A_LOPG(func_ast));
2929 if (STYPEG(func) == ST_MEMBER && CLASSG(func) && CCSYMG(func) &&
2930 VTABLEG(func)) {
2931 func = VTABLEG(func);
2932 }
2933 sptr = func;
2934 } else if (A_TYPEG(arg_gbl.lhs) == A_SUBSCR) {
2935 sptr = sptr_of_subscript(arg_gbl.lhs);
2936 } else {
2937 sptr = sym_of_ast(arg_gbl.lhs);
2938 }
2939 temp_sptr = sym_get_scalar(SYMNAME(sptr), "scl", A_DTYPEG(retval));
2940 temp_ast = mk_id(temp_sptr);
2941 astnew = mk_assn_stmt(temp_ast, retval, 0);
2942 add_stmt_before(astnew, arg_gbl.std);
2943 retval = temp_ast;
2944 }
2945
2946 return retval;
2947}
2948
2949/* func_ast is an intrinsic that might be computed directly into its LHS
2950 * (e.g. TRANPOSE, SPREAD, UNPACK).
2951 * If lhs has an allocatable member, compute into a temp and return it.
2952 * Otherwise return 0.
2953 * This allows allocatable assignments to be handled correctly.
2954 */
2955static int
2956rewrite_intr_allocatable(int func_ast, int func_args, int lhs)
2957{
2958 if (!ast_has_allocatable_member(lhs)) {
2959 return 0;
2960 } else {
2961 /* compute into a temp and copy that to lhs to handle allocatables */
2962 int new_rhs, assn_ast;
2963 int subscr[MAXSUBS];
2964 int tmp_ast = 0;
2965 DTYPE dtype = A_DTYPEG(func_ast);
2966 int tmp_sptr = mk_result_sptr(func_ast, func_args, subscr, DTY(dtype + 1),
2967 lhs, &tmp_ast);
2968 assert(tmp_sptr != 0, "sptr=0 from mk_result_sptr", 0, ERR_Fatal);
2969 assert(tmp_ast != 0, "tmp_ast=0 from mk_result_sptr", 0, ERR_Fatal);
2970 mk_mem_allocate(mk_id(tmp_sptr), subscr, arg_gbl.std, 0);
2971 mk_mem_deallocate(mk_id(tmp_sptr), arg_gbl.std);
2972 new_rhs = rewrite_func_ast(func_ast, func_args, tmp_ast);
2973 if (new_rhs != 0) {
2974 assn_ast = mk_assn_stmt(tmp_ast, new_rhs, dtype);
2975 add_stmt_before(assn_ast, arg_gbl.std);
2976 }
2977 return tmp_ast;
2978 }
2979}
2980
2981static LOGICAL
2982ast_has_allocatable_member(int ast)
2983{
2984 if (ast == 0) {
2985 return FALSE;
2986 } else {
2987 int sptr = memsym_of_ast(ast);
2988 return !HCCSYMG(sptr) && allocatable_member(sptr);
2989 }
2990}
2991
2992/* take out user-defined function to eliminate multiple invocation of function
2993 */
2994static LOGICAL
2995take_out_user_def_func(int func_ast)
2996{
2997 if (A_TYPEG(func_ast) == A_FUNC && arg_gbl.lhs != 0 &&
2998 A_SHAPEG(arg_gbl.lhs) != 0 && !arg_gbl.inforall) {
2999 return TRUE;
3000 }
3001
3002 /* if the function call is in a difficult statement, like an IF or
3003 * DO or computed GOTO, difficult.continue_std holds the temporary
3004 * CONTINUE statement inserted around which temp statements were
3005 * inserted, and difficult.func_std holds the original statement.
3006 * If any statements were inserted between the CONTINUE and the original
3007 * statement, these statements should follow the function call,
3008 * so we must move the function call, store the result, and then
3009 * use the result in the IF, DO, etc. */
3010 if (difficult.continue_std != 0 && difficult.func_std != 0 &&
3011 STD_NEXT(difficult.continue_std) != difficult.func_std) {
3012 return TRUE;
3013 }
3014 return FALSE;
3015}
3016
3017/*
3018 * Create an alloctable char temp of length 'len' within the context of
3019 * of a statement. The temp's len assignment and allocate statements are
3020 * added before 'std'; the temp's deallocate statement is added after 'std'.
3021 */
3022static int
3023alloc_char_temp(int basetype, const char *basename, int len, int std,
3024 int use_basetype)
3025{
3026 int dtype;
3027 int tempsptr;
3028 int tempast;
3029 int tempbase, templen, alloc, lenasn;
3030
3031 if (!use_basetype)
3032 dtype = get_type(2, DTY(basetype), len);
3033 else
3034 dtype = basetype;
3035 tempsptr = get_next_sym(basename, "c");
3036 DTYPEP(tempsptr, dtype);
3037 STYPEP(tempsptr, ST_VAR);
3038 DCLDP(tempsptr, 1);
3039 SCP(tempsptr, SC_BASED);
3040 tempast = mk_id(tempsptr);
3041
3042 /* create a pointer variable */
3043 tempbase = get_next_sym(SYMNAME(tempsptr), "cp");
3044 templen = get_next_sym(SYMNAME(tempsptr), "cl");
3045
3046 /* make the pointer point to sptr */
3047 STYPEP(tempbase, ST_VAR);
3048 DTYPEP(tempbase, DT_PTR);
3049 SCP(tempbase, symutl.sc);
3050
3051 /* set length variable */
3052 STYPEP(templen, ST_VAR);
3053 DTYPEP(templen, DT_INT);
3054 SCP(templen, symutl.sc);
3055
3056 MIDNUMP(tempsptr, tempbase);
3057 CVLENP(tempsptr, templen);
3058 ADJLENP(tempsptr, 1);
3059
3060 /* add char length variable assignment */
3061 lenasn = mk_assn_stmt(mk_id(templen), len, 0);
3062 add_stmt_before(lenasn, std);
3063
3064 /* add an allocate statement */
3065 alloc = mk_stmt(A_ALLOC, 0);
3066 A_TKNP(alloc, TK_ALLOCATE);
3067 A_LOPP(alloc, 0);
3068 A_SRCP(alloc, tempast);
3069 add_stmt_before(alloc, std);
3070
3071 alloc = mk_stmt(A_ALLOC, 0);
3072 A_TKNP(alloc, TK_DEALLOCATE);
3073 A_LOPP(alloc, 0);
3074 A_SRCP(alloc, tempast);
3075 add_stmt_after(alloc, std);
3076
3077 return tempast;
3078}
3079
3080static int
3081get_charintrin_temp(int arg, const char *nm)
3082{
3083 int adt;
3084 int dtype;
3085 int shape;
3086 int temp;
3087 int ast;
3088 int len;
3089
3090 adt = A_DTYPEG(arg);
3091 dtype = adjust_ch_length(adt, arg);
3092 shape = A_SHAPEG(arg);
3093
3094 /* get the temp and add the necessary statements */
3095 if (shape) {
3096 int subscr[MAXSUBS];
3097 /* need to put this into a temp */
3098
3099 temp = mk_shape_sptr(shape, subscr, dtype);
3100 ast = mk_id(temp);
3101 if (ALLOCG(temp)) {
3102 mk_mem_allocate(ast, subscr, arg_gbl.std, 0);
3103 mk_mem_deallocate(ast, arg_gbl.std);
3104 }
3105 } else if (A_ALIASG(DTY(dtype + 1))) {
3106 temp = get_next_sym(nm, "c");
3107 DTYPEP(temp, dtype);
3108 STYPEP(temp, ST_VAR);
3109 DCLDP(temp, 1);
3110 SCP(temp, symutl.sc);
3111 ast = mk_id(temp);
3112 } else {
3113 if (A_TYPEG(arg) == A_ID) {
3114 /* check if arg has early spec */
3115 int sptr = A_SPTRG(arg);
3116 if (sptr && (EARLYSPECG(sptr) ||
3117 (HCCSYMG(sptr) && ADJLENG(sptr) && CVLENG(sptr)))) {
3118 int clen = CVLENG(sptr);
3119 ast = alloc_char_temp(dtype, "trim", mk_id(clen), arg_gbl.std, 1);
3120 return ast;
3121 }
3122 }
3123 len = rewrite_sub_ast(DTY(dtype + 1), 0);
3124 ast = alloc_char_temp(dtype, nm, len, arg_gbl.std, 1);
3125 }
3126
3127 return ast;
3128}

3131 * if there is communication from src to destination.

3133 * and alignment and assign src to that temp and return the temp.
3134 */
3135
3136static int
3137misalignment(int dest, int src, int std)
3138{
3139 return src;
3140}

3142/* arr: array ast */
3143/* arg_ast: call ast */
3144/* argn: argument number */
3145static void
3146check_assumed_size(int arr, int arg_ast, int argn)
3147{
3148 /* In the presence of an interface, need to check if the formal
3149 * argument is assumed-size, and mark the array sequential. */
3150}
3151
3152static int rewrite_sub_args(int arg_ast, int lc);
3153
3154/* keep track of which dimensions have been as dim= for CSHIFT/EOSHIFT calls */
3155static int inshift[8] = {0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0};
3156
3157/*
3158 * return '1' for a simple reference (scalar, member, array element)
3159 * return '1' for unary or binary op of simple reference operands
3160 * return '0' otherwise
3161 */
3162static int
3163simple_reference(int ast)
3164{
3165 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
3166 case A_MEM:
3167 case A_ID:
3168 case A_SUBSCR:
3169 case A_CNST:
3170 return 1;
3171 case A_BINOP:
3172 if (!simple_reference(A_LOPG(ast)))
3173 return 0;
3174 if (!simple_reference(A_ROPG(ast)))
3175 return 0;
3176 return 1;
3177 case A_UNOP:
3178 case A_PAREN:
3179 if (!simple_reference(A_LOPG(ast)))
3180 return 0;
3181 return 1;
3182 default:
3183 return 0;
3184 }
3185} /* simple_reference */
3186
3187/*
3188 * return '1' if the argument should not be rewritten;
3189 * This occurs for nested CSHIFT or EOSHIFT calls.
3190 * in that case, call rewrite_sub_args for the nested call.
3191 */
3192static int
3193leave_arg(int ast, int i, int *parg, int lc)
3194{
3195 int arg;
3196 arg = *parg;
3197 /* 'ast', the calling ast, must be EOSHIFT or CSHIFT
3198 * if the first argument is also EOSHIFT or CSHIFT, return 1 */
3199 if (ast && (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_INTR) &&
3200 (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_EOSHIFT || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_CSHIFT) && (i == 0) &&
3201 (arg) && (A_TYPEG(arg) == A_INTR) &&
3202 (A_OPTYPEG(arg) == I_EOSHIFT || A_OPTYPEG(arg) == I_CSHIFT)) {
3203 int astarglist, argarglist, astdim = 0, argdim = 0, save;
3204 astarglist = A_ARGSG(ast);
3205 argarglist = A_ARGSG(arg);
3206
3207 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_CSHIFT) {
3208 astdim = ARGT_ARG(astarglist, 2);
3209 } else if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_EOSHIFT) {
3210 astdim = ARGT_ARG(astarglist, 3);
3211 }
3212 if (astdim == 0) {
3213 astdim = 1;
3214 } else {
3215 assert(A_TYPEG(astdim) == A_CNST,
3216 "inline_shifts: variable dim not implemented", ast, 3);
3217 astdim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(astdim)));
3218 }
3219 if (A_OPTYPEG(arg) == I_CSHIFT) {
3220 argdim = ARGT_ARG(argarglist, 2);
3221 } else if (A_OPTYPEG(arg) == I_EOSHIFT) {
3222 argdim = ARGT_ARG(argarglist, 3);
3223 }
3224 if (argdim == 0) {
3225 argdim = 1;
3226 } else {
3227 assert(A_TYPEG(argdim) == A_CNST,
3228 "inline_shifts: variable dim not implemented", ast, 3);
3229 argdim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(argdim)));
3230 }
3231 save = inshift[astdim];
3232 inshift[astdim] = 1;
3233 if (inshift[argdim]) {
3234 /* there may be further nested shifts as well */
3235 arg = rewrite_sub_ast(arg, lc);
3236 *parg = arg;
3237 } else {
3238 int args;
3239 args = rewrite_sub_args(arg, lc);
3240 A_ARGSP(arg, args);
3241 }
3242 inshift[astdim] = save;
3243 return 1;
3244 }
3245 if (!XBIT(70, 0x200000) && ast && (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_INTR)) {
3246 int astdim, dim, args, dtype, mask;
3247 mask = 0;
3248 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
3249 case I_SUM:
3250 case I_PRODUCT:
3251 case I_MAXVAL:
3252 case I_MINVAL:
3253 case I_ALL:
3254 case I_ANY:
3255 case I_COUNT:
3256 if (i != 0)
3257 return 0;
3258 args = A_ARGSG(ast);
3259 astdim = ARGT_ARG(args, 1);
3260 mask = ARGT_ARG(args, 2);
3261 break;
3262 case I_NORM2:
3263 if (i != 0)
3264 return 0;
3265 // Argument with expression has to be rewritten
3266 switch(A_TYPEG(arg)) {
3267 default:
3268 break;
3269 case A_BINOP:
3270 case A_UNOP:
3271 case A_PAREN:
3272 return 0;
3273 }
3274
3275 args = A_ARGSG(ast);
3276 astdim = ARGT_ARG(args, 1);
3277 break;
3278 case I_DOT_PRODUCT:
3279 if (i > 1)
3280 return 0;
3281 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3282 if (DT_ISCMPLX(DDTG(dtype)) && (XBIT(70, 0x4000000)
3283 || DDTG(dtype) == DT_QCMPLX
3284 ))
3285 return 0;
3286 astdim = 0;
3287 break;
3288 default:
3289 return 0;
3290 }
3291 if (mask)
3292 return 0;
3293 /* for a reduction function, 1st argument, leave it alone
3294 * if the 'dim' argument (if any) is '1' */
3295 if (astdim != 0) {
3296 if (A_TYPEG(astdim) != A_CNST)
3297 return 0;
3298 if (!XBIT(70, 0x400000)) {
3299 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(astdim));
3300 if (dim != 1)
3301 return 0;
3302 }
3303 }
3304 /* make sure the argument is an array, or expression of array
3305 * (no function calls) */
3306 if (!simple_reference(arg)) {
3307 return 0;
3308 }
3309 return 1;
3310 }
3311 return 0;
3312} /* leave_arg */
3313
3314/*
3315 * return TRUE for TRANSPOSE, and for 1st argument of SPREAD
3316 * these arguments can be left as expressions
3317 */
3318static LOGICAL
3319leave_elemental_argument(int func_ast, int argnum)
3320{
3321 if (A_TYPEG(func_ast) == A_INTR) {
3322 if (A_OPTYPEG(func_ast) == I_TRANSPOSE ||
3323 (A_OPTYPEG(func_ast) == I_SPREAD && argnum == 0)) {
3324 return TRUE;
3325 }
3326 }
3327 return FALSE;
3328} /* leave_elemental_argument */
3329
3330/*
3331 * if the actual argument is a scalar of intrinsic type
3332 * and the dummy argument is a pass-by-reference intent(in) argument,
3333 * then copy the scalar to a temp
3334 */
3335static int
3336copy_scalar_intent_in(int arg, int dummy_sptr, int std)
3337{
3338 int dtype, sptr, newsptr, destast, asnast;
3339 if (!dummy_sptr)
3340 return arg;
3341 if (INTENTG(dummy_sptr) != INTENT_IN)
3342 return arg;
3343 if (PASSBYVALG(dummy_sptr))
3344 return arg;
3345 if (ALLOCATTRG(dummy_sptr))
3346 return arg;
3347 if (POINTERG(dummy_sptr))
3348 return arg;
3349 if (OPTARGG(dummy_sptr))
3350 return arg;
3351 if (ALLOCG(dummy_sptr))
3352 return arg;
3353 dtype = A_DTYPEG(arg);
3354 if (!DT_ISBASIC(dtype))
3355 return arg;
3356 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_CHAR)
3357 return arg;
3358 if (A_SHAPEG(arg))
3359 return arg;
3360 if (A_TYPEG(arg) != A_ID)
3361 return arg;
3362 sptr = A_SPTRG(arg);
3363 if (OPTARGG(sptr))
3364 return arg; /* may be a missing argument */
3365 newsptr = sym_get_scalar(SYMNAME(sptr), "a", dtype);
3366 destast = mk_id(newsptr);
3367 asnast = mk_assn_stmt(destast, arg, dtype);
3368 add_stmt_before(asnast, std);
3369 return mk_id(newsptr);
3370} /* copy_scalar_intent_in */
3371
3372/*
3373 * rewrite arguments of a function or subroutine call
3374 */
3375static int
3376rewrite_sub_args(int arg_ast, int lc)
3377{
3378 int argt;
3379 int newargt = 0;
3380 int arg, subarg;
3381 int shape;
3382 int nargs;
3383 int i, j, n;
3384 int asd;
3385 int temp_arr;
3386 int dtype, eldtype;
3387 int asn_ast;
3388 int ast;
3389 int std;
3390 int arr;
3391 int subscr[MAXSUBS];
3392 int func_args;
3393 int retval;
3394 int dscptr;
3395 int dummy_sptr;
3396 int func_sptr;
3397 int iface;
3398 LOGICAL caller_copies;
3399 int cloc_ast;
3400
3401 std = arg_gbl.std;
3402 argt = A_ARGSG(arg_ast);
3403 nargs = A_ARGCNTG(arg_ast);
3404 func_sptr = procsym_of_ast(A_LOPG(arg_ast));
3405 if (STYPEG(func_sptr) == ST_MEMBER && CLASSG(func_sptr) &&
3406 CCSYMG(func_sptr) && VTABLEG(func_sptr)) {
3407 func_sptr = VTABLEG(func_sptr);
3408 }
3409 proc_arginfo(func_sptr, NULL, &dscptr, &iface);
3410 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
3411 for (i = 0; i < nargs; ++i) {
3412 if (ARGT_ARG(argt, i) == 0) {
3413 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = 0;
3414 continue;
3415 }
3416 caller_copies = FALSE;
3417 arg = ARGT_ARG(argt, i);
3418 dummy_sptr = 0;
3419 if (dscptr && i < PARAMCTG(func_sptr))
3420 dummy_sptr = aux.dpdsc_base[dscptr + i];
3421 if (leave_arg(arg_ast, i, &arg, lc)) {
3422 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3423 continue;
3424 }
3425 /* iso_c c_loc , c_funloc are noops as function arguments:
3426 pass their arg up to this func as an arg
3427 */
3428 if (is_iso_cloc(arg)) {
3429 cloc_ast = ARGT_ARG(A_ARGSG(arg), 0);
3430 /* take out CLOC for both byval and byref arguments */
3431 if ((dummy_sptr == 0) || (func_sptr == 0)) {
3432
3433 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = cloc_ast;
3434 continue;
3435 }
3436 }
3437
3438 if (A_TYPEG(arg_ast) == A_INTR && A_OPTYPEG(arg_ast) == I_DOT_PRODUCT &&
3439 i == 2 && arg == ARGT_ARG(argt, 0)) {
3440 /* optimize the case of DOTPRODUCT(a(:)%mem,a(:)%mem) */
3441 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0);
3442 continue;
3443 }
3444 arg = rewrite_sub_ast(arg, lc);
3445 /* arg = rewrite_interface_args(arg_ast, arg, i);*/
3446 /* leave elementals alone */
3447 if (A_TYPEG(arg_ast) == A_INTR && INKINDG(func_sptr) == IK_ELEMENTAL) {
3448 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3449 continue;
3450 }
3451 /* leave pointer assign alone */
3452 if (A_TYPEG(arg_ast) == A_ICALL && A_OPTYPEG(arg_ast) == I_PTR2_ASSIGN) {
3453 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3454 continue;
3455 }
3456 if (A_TYPEG(arg_ast) == A_INTR) {
3457 /* leave elementals alone, leave pointer assign alone */
3458 if (INKINDG(func_sptr) == IK_ELEMENTAL ||
3459 A_OPTYPEG(arg_ast) == I_PTR2_ASSIGN) {
3460 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3461 continue;
3462 }
3463 }
3464 if (iface && ELEMENTALG(iface)) {
3465 /* leave alone if arg is not an elemental function,
3466 * else process function below
3467 */
3468 if (A_TYPEG(arg) == A_FUNC) {
3469 int sym;
3470 switch (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(arg))) {
3471 case A_ID:
3472 case A_LABEL:
3473 case A_ENTRY:
3474 case A_SUBSCR:
3475 case A_SUBSTR:
3476 case A_MEM:
3477 sym = memsym_of_ast(A_LOPG(arg));
3478 if (CLASSG(sym) && VTABLEG(sym) && BINDG(sym)) {
3479 sym = VTABLEG(sym);
3480 break;
3481 }
3482 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
3483 default:
3484 sym = A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(arg));
3485 }
3486 if (ELEMENTALG(sym)) {
3487 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3488 continue;
3489 }
3490 } else if (A_TYPEG(arg) != A_FUNC || !ELEMENTALG(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(arg)))) {
3491 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3492 continue;
3493 }
3494 }
3495 /* don't touch %val, %loc, and %ref operators even their shape is
3496 * not NULL
3497 */
3498 if (A_TYPEG(arg) == A_UNOP) {
3499 if (A_OPTYPEG(arg) == OP_VAL || A_OPTYPEG(arg) == OP_BYVAL ||
3500 A_OPTYPEG(arg) == OP_LOC || A_OPTYPEG(arg) == OP_REF) {
3501 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3502 continue;
3503 }
3504 }
3505 /* if this is a scalar expression variable passed to
3506 * a non-value intent(in) argument, copy to a temp
3507 * so we don't have to mark the variable as ADDRTKN */
3508 if (dummy_sptr && XBIT(68, 8))
3509 arg = copy_scalar_intent_in(arg, dummy_sptr, std);
3510 shape = A_SHAPEG(arg);
3511 dtype = A_DTYPEG(arg);
3512 subarg = arg;
3513 if (A_TYPEG(subarg) == A_SUBSTR)
3514 subarg = A_LOPG(subarg);
3515 if (A_TYPEG(subarg) == A_ID) {
3516 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3517 continue;
3518 }
3519 if (A_TYPEG(subarg) == A_MEM) {
3520 /* if this is an array of derived types, then it needs
3521 * to be rewritten */
3522 if (A_SHAPEG(A_PARENTG(subarg))) {
3523 caller_copies = TRUE;
3524 goto rewrite_this;
3525 }
3526 if (A_TYPEG(A_MEMG(subarg)) == A_ID) {
3527 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3528 continue;
3529 }
3530 }
3531 if (shape) {
3532 /* for transpose(elementalexpression) or
3533 * spread(elementalexpression,dim,size),
3534 * leave the elemental expressions in place, don't assign
3535 * to a temp. They will be expanded when the transpose or spread
3536 * are inlined */
3537 if (leave_elemental_argument(arg_ast, i)) {
3538 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3539 continue;
3540 }
3541 /* argument may be an array, but not a whole array */
3542 /* check for a(:)%b(9) */
3543 if (A_TYPEG(subarg) == A_SUBSCR) {
3544 int lop = A_LOPG(subarg);
3545 if (A_TYPEG(lop) == A_MEM && A_SHAPEG(A_PARENTG(lop))) {
3546 /* shape comes from parent of A_MEM; copy */
3547 caller_copies = TRUE;
3548 goto rewrite_this;
3549 }
3550 }
3551
3552 /* need to check for vector subscripts here */
3553 if (subarg == arg && A_TYPEG(subarg) == A_SUBSCR) {
3554 asd = A_ASDG(subarg);
3555 n = ASD_NDIM(asd);
3556 for (j = 0; j < n; ++j)
3557 if (A_TYPEG(ASD_SUBS(asd, j)) != A_TRIPLE &&
3558 A_SHAPEG(ASD_SUBS(asd, j)) != 0)
3559 goto rewrite_this;
3560 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3561 continue;
3562 }
3563 rewrite_this:
3564 assert(!arg_gbl.inforall, "rewrite_sub_args: can not handle PURE arg",
3565 arg, 2);
3566 if (arg_gbl.inforall) {
3567 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3568 continue;
3569 }
3570
3571 /* either vector subscript, or array expression */
3572 /* need to put this into a temp */
3573 ast = search_conform_array(subarg, FALSE);
3574 if (ast == 0)
3575 ast = search_conform_array(subarg, TRUE);
3576 assert(ast != 0, "rewrite_sub_args: can't find array", arg, 4);
3577 eldtype = DDTG(dtype);
3578 if (eldtype == DT_ASSCHAR || eldtype == DT_ASSNCHAR ||
3579 eldtype == DT_DEFERCHAR || eldtype == DT_DEFERNCHAR) {
3580 /* make up fake datatype with actual length */
3581 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_INTR) {
3582 eldtype =
3583 fix_dtype(memsym_of_ast(ARGT_ARG(A_ARGSG(ast), 0)), eldtype);
3584 } else {
3585 eldtype = get_type(2, DTY(eldtype), string_expr_length(arg));
3586 }
3587 }
3588
3589 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_INTR) {
3590 func_args = A_ARGSG(ast);
3591 temp_arr = mk_result_sptr(ast, func_args, subscr, eldtype, 0, &retval);
3592 ast = retval;
3593 } else {
3594 temp_arr = mk_assign_sptr(ast, "a", subscr, eldtype, &ast);
3595 }
3596 /* make assignment to temp_arr */
3597 asn_ast = mk_assn_stmt(ast, arg, dtype);
3598 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = ast;
3599 if (ALLOCG(temp_arr)) {
3600 mk_mem_allocate(mk_id(temp_arr), subscr, std, 0);
3601 }
3602 add_stmt_before(asn_ast, std);
3603 if (ALLOCG(temp_arr))
3604 mk_mem_deallocate(mk_id(temp_arr), std);
3605 if (caller_copies && (!dummy_sptr || INTENTG(dummy_sptr) != INTENT_IN)) {
3606 /* make assignment from temp_arr */
3607
3608 asn_ast = mk_assn_stmt(arg, ast, dtype);
3609 add_stmt_after(asn_ast, std);
3610 }
3611 } else if (A_TYPEG(subarg) == A_SUBSCR) {
3612 /*
3613 * argument is a subscripted reference. If the array is
3614 * distributed, then this needs to be put into a scalar temp
3615 * before the call and copied back to the array element after
3616 * the call. Note, this should probably be done in a later
3617 * phase
3618 */
3619
3620 arr = A_LOPG(subarg);
3621 check_assumed_size(arr, arg_ast, i);
3622 if (A_TYPEG(arr) != A_ID || !ALIGNG(A_SPTRG(arr)))
3623 goto lval;
3624 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = subarg;
3625 } else if (A_ISLVAL(A_TYPEG(subarg))) {
3626 lval:
3627 /* This reference is an lvalue. We want to leave it alone.
3628 * However, it may be necessary to pull out subcomponents
3629 * of it. Example: substr(idx(1):idx(2)) where idx is distributed.
3630 */
3631 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3632 } else
3633 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = arg;
3634 }
3635 return newargt;
3636}
3637
3638/*
3639 * rewrite subprogram call
3640 */
3641static int
3642rewrite_sub_ast(int ast, int lc)
3643{
3644 int shape;
3645 int l, r, lop;
3646 int dtype;
3647 int args;
3648 int asd;
3649 int numdim;
3650 int i;
3651 int subs[MAXSUBS];
3652
3653 if (ast == 0)
3654 return 0;
3655 shape = A_SHAPEG(ast);
3656 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
3657 case A_NULL:
3658 case A_CMPLXC:
3659 case A_CNST:
3660 case A_ID:
3661 case A_LABEL:
3662 return ast;
3663 case A_MP_ATOMICREAD:
3664 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3665 r = rewrite_sub_ast(A_SRCG(ast), lc);
3666 r = mk_atomic(A_MP_ATOMICREAD, 0, r, dtype);
3667 A_MEM_ORDERP(r, A_MEM_ORDERG(ast));
3668 return r;
3669 case A_MEM:
3670 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3671 r = rewrite_sub_ast((int)A_MEMG(ast), lc);
3672 l = rewrite_sub_ast(A_PARENTG(ast), lc);
3673 return mk_member(l, r, dtype);
3674 case A_BINOP:
3675 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3676 l = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LOPG(ast), lc);
3677 r = rewrite_sub_ast(A_ROPG(ast), lc);
3678 return mk_binop(A_OPTYPEG(ast), l, r, dtype);
3679 case A_UNOP:
3680 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3681 l = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LOPG(ast), lc);
3682 return mk_unop(A_OPTYPEG(ast), l, dtype);
3683 case A_PAREN:
3684 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3685 l = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LOPG(ast), lc);
3686 return mk_paren(l, dtype);
3687 case A_CONV:
3688 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3689 l = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LOPG(ast), lc);
3690 /* If the operand is a scalar and the result has a shape, we
3691 * can't use mk_convert */
3692 if (!A_SHAPEG(l) && A_SHAPEG(ast)) {
3693 r = mk_promote_scalar(l, dtype, A_SHAPEG(ast));
3694 A_DTYPEP(r, dtype);
3695 } else
3696 r = mk_convert(l, dtype);
3697 return r;
3698 case A_SUBSTR:
3699 lop = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LOPG(ast), lc);
3700 l = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LEFTG(ast), lc);
3701 r = rewrite_sub_ast(A_RIGHTG(ast), lc);
3702 return mk_substr(lop, l, r, A_DTYPEG(ast));
3703 case A_SUBSCR:
3704 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
3705 asd = A_ASDG(ast);
3706 numdim = ASD_NDIM(asd);
3707 assert(numdim > 0 && numdim <= 7, "rewrite_sub_ast: bad numdim", ast, 4);
3708 for (i = 0; i < numdim; ++i) {
3709 l = rewrite_sub_ast(ASD_SUBS(asd, i), lc);
3710 subs[i] = l;
3711 }
3712 /* return mk_subscr(A_LOPG(ast), subs, numdim, DTY(dtype+1)); */
3713 return mk_subscr(A_LOPG(ast), subs, numdim, dtype);
3714 case A_TRIPLE:
3715 l = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LBDG(ast), lc);
3716 r = rewrite_sub_ast(A_UPBDG(ast), lc);
3717 i = rewrite_sub_ast(A_STRIDEG(ast), lc);
3718 return mk_triple(l, r, i);
3719 case A_INTR:
3720 case A_FUNC:
3721 ast = inline_reduction_f90(ast, 0, lc, NULL);
3722 if (A_TYPEG(ast) != A_INTR && A_TYPEG(ast) != A_FUNC)
3723 return ast;
3724 args = rewrite_sub_args(ast, lc);
3725
3726 /* try again to inline it */
3727 ast = inline_reduction_f90(ast, 0, lc, NULL);
3728 l = rewrite_func_ast(ast, args, 0);
3729 return l;
3730 case A_ICALL:
3731 ast = inline_reduction_f90(ast, 0, lc, NULL);
3732 if (A_TYPEG(ast) != A_ICALL)
3733 return ast;
3734 args = rewrite_sub_args(ast, lc);
3735 A_ARGSP(ast, args);
3736 /* try again to inline it */
3737 ast = inline_reduction_f90(ast, 0, lc, NULL);
3738 l = rewrite_func_ast(ast, args, 0);
3739 return l;
3740 case A_CALL:
3741 assert(elemental_func_call(ast),
3742 "rewrite_sub_ast: attempt to rewrite call to non elemental subr",
3743 ast, 3);
3744 args = rewrite_sub_args(ast, lc);
3745 A_ARGSP(ast, args);
3746 transform_elemental(ast, args);
3747 return -1;
3748 default:
3749 interr("rewrite_sub_ast: unexpected ast", ast, 2);
3750 return ast;
3751 }
3752}
3753
3754/* We are using the lhs for the result of an inline intrinsic.
3755 * Allocate it if necessary. */
3756static void
3757allocate_lhs_if_needed(int lhs, int rhs, int std)
3758{
3759 int astif, new_lhs;
3760 if (!XBIT(54, 1))
3761 return;
3762 if (A_TYPEG(lhs) == A_SUBSCR)
3763 return;
3764 if (!ast_is_sym(lhs) || !ALLOCATTRG(sym_of_ast(lhs)))
3765 return;
3766 astif = mk_conformable_test(lhs, rhs, OP_LE);
3767 add_stmt_before(astif, std);
3768 gen_dealloc_if_allocated(lhs, std);
3769 new_lhs = add_shapely_subscripts(lhs, rhs, A_DTYPEG(rhs),
3770 array_element_dtype(A_DTYPEG(lhs)));
3771 add_stmt_before(mk_allocate(new_lhs), std);
3772 add_stmt_before(mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0), std);
3773}
3774
3775void
3776rewrite_asn(int ast, int std, bool flag, int lc)
3777{
3778 int rhs, lhs;
3779 int args;
3780 int l;
3781 int asd, j, n;
3782 int new_rhs;
3783 LOGICAL doremove;
3784
3785 rhs = A_SRCG(ast);
3786 lhs = A_DESTG(ast);
3787 arg_gbl.lhs = lhs;
3788
3789 lhs = rewrite_sub_ast(A_DESTG(ast), lc);
3790 A_DESTP(ast, lhs);
3791 arg_gbl.lhs = lhs;
3792
3793 if (A_TYPEG(rhs) == A_MP_ATOMICREAD)
3794 return;
3795
3796 /* If this is an assignment of an intrinsic directly into
3797 * the LHS, avoid the temp */
3798 if (flag && A_SHAPEG(lhs) &&
3799 (A_TYPEG(rhs) == A_FUNC || A_TYPEG(rhs) == A_INTR)) {
3800 int std_prev = STD_PREV(std); /* for allocate_lhs_if_needed case */
3801 if (A_TYPEG(lhs) == A_SUBSCR) {
3802 asd = A_ASDG(lhs);
3803 n = ASD_NDIM(asd);
3804 for (j = 0; j < n; ++j)
3805 if (A_TYPEG(ASD_SUBS(asd, j)) != A_TRIPLE &&
3806 A_SHAPEG(ASD_SUBS(asd, j)) != 0)
3807 goto rewrite_this; /* vector subscript */
3808 }
3809 /* Otherwise, we can use lhs directly */
3810 args = rewrite_sub_args(rhs, lc);
3811 A_ARGSP(rhs, args);
3812 new_rhs = inline_reduction_f90(rhs, lhs, lc, &doremove);
3813 if (new_rhs == rhs) {
3814 new_rhs = rewrite_func_ast(rhs, args, lhs);
3815 doremove = new_rhs == 0;
3816 }
3817 if (doremove) {
3818 allocate_lhs_if_needed(lhs, rhs, STD_NEXT(std_prev));
3819 if (std)
3820 delete_stmt(std);
3821 } else {
3822 A_SRCP(ast, new_rhs);
3823 }
3824 return;
3825 }
3826
3827rewrite_this:
3828 l = rewrite_sub_ast(rhs, lc);
3829 A_SRCP(ast, l);
3830}
3831
3832void
3833rewrite_calls(void)
3834{
3835 int std, stdnext, stdnew;
3836 int ast, rhs, lhs, astnew;
3837 int args, a;
3838 int type;
3839 int sptr_lhs;
3840 int prevstd, src;
3841 int parallel_depth;
3842 int task_depth;
3843 /*
3844 * Transform subroutine/function call arguments.
3845 * 1. If they contain array expressions, a temp must be allocated and
3846 * the expression must be copied into the temp.
3847 * 2. If they contain references to array elements, then the elements must
3848 * be copied into a scalar, the scalar passed, and the elements
3849 * copied back. Some of this can be avoided if the INTENT is known.
3850 * 3. Scalars aren't interfered with, except scalar arguments to
3851 * intent(in) dummy arguments are copied to a temp, and the temp
3852 * is passed instead.
3853 */
3854
3855 parallel_depth = 0;
3856 task_depth = 0;
3857 for (std = STD_NEXT(0); std; std = stdnext) {
3858 stdnext = STD_NEXT(std);
3859 arg_gbl.std = std;
3860 arg_gbl.lhs = 0;
3861 arg_gbl.used = FALSE;
3862 arg_gbl.inforall = FALSE;
3863 gbl.lineno = STD_LINENO(std);
3864 ast = STD_AST(std);
3865 switch (type = A_TYPEG(ast)) {
3866 case A_ASN:
3867 rhs = A_SRCG(ast);
3868 if (A_TYPEG(rhs) == A_HOVLPSHIFT || A_TYPEG(rhs) == A_HCSTART)
3869 break;
3870 lhs = A_DESTG(ast);
3871 sptr_lhs = sym_of_ast(lhs);
3872 open_pragma(STD_LINENO(std));
3873 if (expr_dependent(A_SRCG(ast), lhs, std, std))
3874 arg_gbl.used = TRUE;
3875 close_pragma();
3876 rewrite_asn(ast, std, TRUE, 0);
3877 break;
3878 case A_WHERE:
3879 lhs = A_DESTG(A_IFSTMTG(ast));
3880 sptr_lhs = sym_of_ast(lhs);
3881 if (expr_dependent(A_IFEXPRG(ast), lhs, std, std))
3882 arg_gbl.used = TRUE;
3883 assert(A_IFSTMTG(ast), "rewrite_calls: block where", 0, 4);
3884 rewrite_asn(A_IFSTMTG(ast), std, FALSE, 0);
3885 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_IFEXPRG(ast), 0);
3886 A_IFEXPRP(ast, a);
3887 break;
3888 case A_IFTHEN:
3889 case A_IF:
3890 case A_AIF:
3891 case A_ELSEIF:
3892 case A_DOWHILE:
3893 case A_CGOTO:
3894 case A_DO:
3895 case A_MP_PDO:
3896 /* If the expression requires a temporary as part of its
3897 * evaluation, must make sure that the temp is freed before
3898 * the IF statement. Insert a dummy statement, then delete it.
3899 */
3900 astnew = mk_stmt(A_CONTINUE, 0);
3901 stdnew = add_stmt_before(astnew, std);
3902 arg_gbl.std = stdnew;
3903
3904 difficult.continue_std = stdnew;
3905 difficult.func_std = std;
3906 switch (type) {
3907 extern int assign_scalar(int, int); /* vsub.c */
3908 case A_IF:
3909 case A_ELSEIF:
3910 case A_AIF:
3911 case A_DOWHILE:
3912 case A_IFTHEN:
3913 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_IFEXPRG(ast), 0);
3914 A_IFEXPRP(ast, a);
3915 break;
3916 case A_CGOTO:
3917 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LOPG(ast), 0);
3918 A_LOPP(ast, a);
3919 break;
3920 case A_DO:
3921 case A_MP_PDO:
3922 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_M1G(ast), 0);
3923 if (a && contains_call(a)) {
3924 a = assign_scalar(std, a);
3925 }
3926 A_M1P(ast, a);
3927 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_M2G(ast), 0);
3928 if (a && contains_call(a)) {
3929 a = assign_scalar(std, a);
3930 }
3931 A_M2P(ast, a);
3932 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_M3G(ast), 0);
3933 if (a && contains_call(a)) {
3934 a = assign_scalar(std, a);
3935 }
3936 A_M3P(ast, a);
3937 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_M4G(ast), 0);
3938 if (a && contains_call(a)) {
3939 a = assign_scalar(std, a);
3940 }
3941 A_M4P(ast, a);
3942 if (type == A_MP_PDO) {
3943 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LASTVALG(ast), 0);
3944 if (a && contains_call(a)) {
3945 a = assign_scalar(std, a);
3946 }
3947 A_LASTVALP(ast, a);
3948 }
3949 break;
3950 default:
3951 interr("rewrite_calls: unknown control ", ast, 4);
3952 break;
3953 }
3954 difficult.continue_std = difficult.func_std = 0;
3955 /* unlink the dummy statement */
3956 STD_NEXT(STD_PREV(stdnew)) = STD_NEXT(stdnew);
3957 STD_PREV(STD_NEXT(stdnew)) = STD_PREV(stdnew);
3958 arg_gbl.std = std;
3959 break;
3960 case A_ICALL:
3961 if (rewrite_sub_ast(ast, 0) != -1)
3962 ast_to_comment(ast);
3963 break;
3964 case A_CALL:
3965 if (elemental_func_call(ast)) {
3966 if (rewrite_sub_ast(ast, 0) != -1)
3967 ast_to_comment(ast);
3968 } else {
3969 args = rewrite_sub_args(ast, 0);
3970 A_ARGSP(ast, args);
3971 }
3972 break;
3973 case A_ALLOC:
3974 if (A_TKNG(ast) == TK_DEALLOCATE && !A_DALLOCMEMG(ast)) {
3975 if (A_TYPEG(A_SRCG(ast)) == A_SUBSCR) {
3976 A_SRCP(ast, A_LOPG(A_SRCG(ast)));
3977 }
3978 sptr_lhs = memsym_of_ast(A_SRCG(ast));
3979 if (allocatable_member(sptr_lhs)) {
3980 /* Has allocatable members but item itself is not
3981 * allocatable nor pointer
3982 */
3983 bool lhs_not_allocatable =
3984 !ALLOCG(sptr_lhs) && !ALLOCATTRG(sptr_lhs) && !POINTERG(sptr_lhs);
3985 /* HCCSYMG() checks if sptr_lhs is a compiler-generated temporary
3986 * variable or not. It is used inside rewrite_allocatable_assignment()
3987 * to guard handle_allocatable_members() which performs rewriting.
3988 * As a result, compiler-generated temporary allocatable variables
3989 * will only undergo shallow copying. HCCSYMG() is used here to
3990 * prevent deep deallocation for temporary allocatable variables.
3991 */
3992 if (!HCCSYMG(sptr_lhs) || lhs_not_allocatable)
3993 rewrite_deallocate(A_SRCG(ast), false, std);
3994 if (lhs_not_allocatable)
3995 nop_dealloc(sptr_lhs, ast);
3996 }
3997 } else if (A_TKNG(ast) == TK_ALLOCATE) {
3998 int a, sptr2, astmem;
3999 sptr_lhs = memsym_of_ast(A_SRCG(ast));
4000 if (STYPEG(sptr_lhs) == ST_MEMBER) {
4001 astmem = A_SRCG(ast);
4002 } else {
4003 astmem = 0;
4004 }
4005 switch (A_TYPEG(A_STARTG(ast))) {
4006 case A_ID:
4007 case A_LABEL:
4008 case A_ENTRY:
4009 case A_SUBSCR:
4010 case A_SUBSTR:
4011 case A_MEM:
4012 sptr2 = (A_STARTG(ast)) ? memsym_of_ast(A_STARTG(ast)) : 0;
4013 break;
4014 default:
4015 sptr2 = 0;
4016 }
4017 if (sptr2 > NOSYM &&
4018 (CLASSG(sptr2) || (CLASSG(sptr_lhs) && ALLOCATTRG(sptr2)))) {
4019 check_pointer_type(A_SRCG(ast), A_STARTG(ast), std, 1);
4020 } else {
4021 a = A_DTYPEG(ast);
4022 if (DTY(a) == TY_ARRAY)
4023 a = DTY(a + 1);
4024
4025 if (CLASSG(sptr_lhs) || ALLOCDESCG(sptr_lhs) ||
4026 has_tbp_or_final(DTYPEG(sptr_lhs)) || has_tbp_or_final(a) ||
4027 is_or_has_poly(sptr_lhs) ||
4028 has_length_type_parameter_use(DTYPEG(sptr_lhs)) ||
4029 (sptr2 && !ALLOCATTRG(sptr_lhs) && has_poly_mbr(sptr_lhs, 1))) {
4030 int alloc_source;
4031 DTYPE source_dtype;
4032 check_alloc_ptr_type(sptr_lhs, std, a, 1, 1, A_SRCG(ast), astmem);
4033 alloc_source = A_STARTG(ast);
4034 source_dtype = DTYPEG(sptr2);
4035 if (alloc_source > 0 && (DTY(DDTG(source_dtype)) == TY_CHAR ||
4036 DTY(DDTG(source_dtype)) == TY_NCHAR)) {
4037 /* This is a sourced allocation with a character source argument.
4038 * Need to make sure we assign the character object's length to
4039 * the receiver's descriptor.
4040 */
4041 int len = ast_intr(I_LEN, astb.bnd.dtype, 1,
4042 A_TYPEG(alloc_source) == A_SUBSCR ?
4043 A_LOPG(alloc_source) : alloc_source);
4044 len = gen_set_len_ast(A_SRCG(ast), SDSCG(sptr_lhs), len);
4045 add_stmt_after(len, std);
4046 }
4047 }
4048 }
4049 }
4050 break;
4051 case A_ELSEWHERE:
4052 case A_ENDWHERE:
4053 case A_END:
4054 case A_STOP:
4055 case A_RETURN:
4056 case A_ELSE:
4057 case A_ENDIF:
4058 case A_ENDDO:
4059 case A_CONTINUE:
4060 case A_GOTO:
4061 case A_ASNGOTO:
4062 case A_AGOTO:
4063 case A_ENTRY:
4064 case A_PAUSE:
4065 case A_COMMENT:
4066 case A_COMSTR:
4067 case A_REDISTRIBUTE:
4068 case A_REALIGN:
4069 case A_HCFINISH:
4070 case A_MASTER:
4071 case A_ENDMASTER:
4072 case A_CRITICAL:
4073 case A_ENDCRITICAL:
4074 case A_ATOMIC:
4075 case A_ATOMICCAPTURE:
4076 case A_ATOMICREAD:
4077 case A_ATOMICWRITE:
4078 case A_ENDATOMIC:
4079 case A_BARRIER:
4080 case A_NOBARRIER:
4081 case A_MP_CRITICAL:
4082 case A_MP_ENDCRITICAL:
4083 case A_MP_ATOMIC:
4084 case A_MP_ENDATOMIC:
4085 case A_MP_MASTER:
4086 case A_MP_ENDMASTER:
4087 case A_MP_SINGLE:
4088 case A_MP_ENDSINGLE:
4089 case A_MP_BARRIER:
4090 case A_MP_TASKWAIT:
4091 case A_MP_TASKYIELD:
4092 case A_MP_ENDPDO:
4093 case A_MP_ENDSECTIONS:
4094 case A_MP_WORKSHARE:
4095 case A_MP_ENDWORKSHARE:
4096 case A_MP_BPDO:
4097 case A_MP_EPDO:
4098 case A_MP_SECTION:
4099 case A_MP_LSECTION:
4100 case A_MP_PRE_TLS_COPY:
4101 case A_MP_BCOPYIN:
4102 case A_MP_COPYIN:
4103 case A_MP_ECOPYIN:
4104 case A_MP_BCOPYPRIVATE:
4105 case A_MP_COPYPRIVATE:
4106 case A_MP_ECOPYPRIVATE:
4107 case A_MP_EMPSCOPE:
4108 case A_MP_BORDERED:
4109 case A_MP_EORDERED:
4110 case A_MP_FLUSH:
4111 case A_MP_TASKGROUP:
4112 case A_MP_ETASKGROUP:
4113 case A_MP_DISTRIBUTE:
4114 case A_MP_ENDDISTRIBUTE:
4115 case A_MP_ENDTARGETDATA:
4116 case A_MP_TASKREG:
4117 case A_MP_TASKDUP:
4118 case A_MP_ETASKDUP:
4119 break;
4120 case A_MP_TASKLOOPREG:
4121 case A_MP_ETASKLOOPREG:
4122 break;
4123 case A_MP_TASK:
4124 case A_MP_TASKLOOP:
4125 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_IFPARG(ast), 0);
4126 A_IFPARP(ast, a);
4127 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_FINALPARG(ast), 0);
4128 A_FINALPARP(ast, a);
4129 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_PRIORITYG(ast), 0);
4130 A_PRIORITYP(ast, a);
4131 ++task_depth;
4132 set_descriptor_sc(SC_PRIVATE);
4133 break;
4134 case A_MP_ENDTASK:
4135 case A_MP_ETASKLOOP:
4136 --task_depth;
4137 if (parallel_depth == 0 && task_depth == 0) {
4138 set_descriptor_sc(SC_LOCAL);
4139 }
4140 break;
4141 case A_MP_BMPSCOPE:
4142 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_STBLKG(ast), 0);
4143 A_STBLKP(ast, a);
4144 break;
4145 case A_MP_TASKFIRSTPRIV:
4146 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LOPG(ast), 0);
4147 A_LOPP(ast, a);
4148 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_ROPG(ast), 0);
4149 A_ROPP(ast, a);
4150 break;
4151 case A_MP_PARALLEL:
4152 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_IFPARG(ast), 0);
4153 A_IFPARP(ast, a);
4154 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_NPARG(ast), 0);
4155 A_NPARP(ast, a);
4156 /* proc_bind is constant
4157 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_PROCBINDG(ast), 0);
4158 A_PROCBINDP(ast, a);
4159 */
4160 ++parallel_depth;
4161 /*symutl.sc = SC_PRIVATE;*/
4162 set_descriptor_sc(SC_PRIVATE);
4163 break;
4164 case A_MP_TEAMS:
4165 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_NTEAMSG(ast), 0);
4166 A_NTEAMSP(ast, a);
4167 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_THRLIMITG(ast), 0);
4168 A_THRLIMITP(ast, a);
4169 break;
4170 case A_MP_ENDPARALLEL:
4171 --parallel_depth;
4172 if (parallel_depth == 0 && task_depth == 0) {
4173 /*symutl.sc = SC_LOCAL;*/
4174 set_descriptor_sc(SC_LOCAL);
4175 }
4176 break;
4177 case A_MP_ATOMICREAD:
4178 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_SRCG(ast), 0);
4179 A_SRCP(ast, a);
4180 break;
4181 case A_MP_ATOMICWRITE:
4182 case A_MP_ATOMICUPDATE:
4183 case A_MP_ATOMICCAPTURE:
4184 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LOPG(ast), 0);
4185 A_LOPP(ast, a);
4186 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_ROPG(ast), 0);
4187 A_ROPP(ast, a);
4188 break;
4189 case A_MP_ENDTEAMS:
4190 case A_MP_ENDTARGET:
4191 case A_MP_TARGET:
4192 break;
4193 case A_MP_CANCEL:
4194 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_IFPARG(ast), 0);
4195 A_IFPARP(ast, a);
4196 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
4197 case A_MP_SECTIONS:
4198 case A_MP_CANCELLATIONPOINT:
4199 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_ENDLABG(ast), 0);
4200 A_ENDLABP(ast, a);
4201 break;
4202 case A_MP_TARGETDATA:
4203 case A_MP_TARGETENTERDATA:
4204 case A_MP_TARGETEXITDATA:
4205 case A_MP_TARGETUPDATE:
4206 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_IFPARG(ast), 0);
4207 A_IFPARP(ast, a);
4208 break;
4209 case A_FORALL:
4210 arg_gbl.used = TRUE; /* don't use lhs for intrinsics */
4211 arg_gbl.inforall = TRUE;
4212 src = A_SRCG(ast);
4213 prevstd = STD_PREV(std);
4214 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_IFEXPRG(ast), 0);
4215 A_IFEXPRP(ast, a);
4216 rewrite_asn(A_IFSTMTG(ast), std, TRUE, 0);
4217 arg_gbl.inforall = FALSE;
4218
4219 /* there is no std created from forall before, if it is
4220 * created now, show the first one */
4221 if (src == 0 && STD_PREV(std) != prevstd) {
4222 A_SRCP(ast, STD_NEXT(prevstd));
4223 assert(STD_NEXT(prevstd) != std, "rewrite_calls: something is wrong",
4224 std, 3);
4225 }
4226 break;
4227 case A_HLOCALIZEBNDS:
4228 case A_HCYCLICLP:
4229 lhs = A_LOPG(ast);
4230 assert(A_TYPEG(lhs) == A_ID, "rewrite_calls: id not found", ast, 3);
4231 sptr_lhs = A_SPTRG(lhs);
4232 assert(STYPEG(sptr_lhs) == ST_ARRDSC || STYPEG(sptr_lhs) == ST_ARRAY,
4233 "rewrite_calls: array not found", ast, 3);
4234 break;
4235 case A_HGETSCLR:
4236 case A_HOWNERPROC:
4237 break;
4238 case A_PREFETCH:
4239 break;
4240 case A_PRAGMA:
4241 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_LOPG(ast), 0);
4242 A_LOPP(ast, a);
4243 a = rewrite_sub_ast(A_ROPG(ast), 0);
4244 A_ROPP(ast, a);
4245 break;
4246 case A_MP_EMAP:
4247 case A_MP_MAP:
4248 case A_MP_TARGETLOOPTRIPCOUNT:
4249 case A_MP_EREDUCTION:
4250 case A_MP_BREDUCTION:
4251 case A_MP_REDUCTIONITEM:
4252 break;
4253 default:
4254 interr("rewrite_subroutine: unknown stmt found", ast, 4);
4255 break;
4256 }
4257 }
4258}
4259
4260static void
4261nop_dealloc(int sptr, int ast)
4262{
4263 if (SCG(sptr) == SC_LOCAL && AUTOBJG(sptr) && has_allocattr(sptr))
4264 return;
4265 ast_to_comment(ast);
4266}
4267
4268/*
4269 * call pghpf_reduce_descriptor(result$sd, kind, len, array$sd, dim)
4270 *
4271 * set up result descriptor for reduction intrinsic -- used when the
4272 * dim arg is variable. result dimensions are aligned with the
4273 * corresponding source dimensions and the result array becomes
4274 * replicated over the reduction dimension.
4275 */
4276
4277static void
4278add_reduce_descriptor(int temp_sptr, int arr_sptr, int arr_ast, int dim)
4279{
4280 DTYPE dtype = DTYPEG(temp_sptr);
4281 int kind = mk_cval(dtype_to_arg(DTY(dtype + 1)), astb.bnd.dtype);
4282 int len = size_ast(temp_sptr, DDTG(dtype));
4283 int sptrFunc = sym_mkfunc_nodesc(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_reduce_descriptor), 0);
4284 int astStmt = begin_call(A_CALL, sptrFunc, 5);
4285 add_arg(mk_id(DESCRG(temp_sptr)));
4286 add_arg(kind);
4287 add_arg(len);
4288 add_arg(check_member(arr_ast, mk_id(DESCRG(arr_sptr))));
4289 add_arg(convert_int(dim, astb.bnd.dtype));
4290 add_stmt_before(astStmt, arg_gbl.std);
4291}
4292
4293/* call pghpf_spread_descriptor(result$sd, source$sd, dim, ncopies)
4294 *
4295 * set up result descriptor for spread intrinsic -- used when the dim
4296 * arg is variable. the added spread dimension is given a collapsed
4297 * distribution and the remaining dimensions are aligned with the
4298 * corresponding source dimensions. overlap allowances are set to
4299 * zero.
4300 */
4301
4302static void
4303add_spread_descriptor(int temp_sptr, int arr_sptr, int arr_ast, int dim,
4304 int ncopies)
4305{
4306 int sptrFunc;
4307 int astStmt;
4308
4309 dim = convert_int(dim, astb.bnd.dtype);
4310 ncopies = convert_int(ncopies, astb.bnd.dtype);
4311 sptrFunc = sym_mkfunc_nodesc(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_spread_descriptor), 0);
4312 astStmt = begin_call(A_CALL, sptrFunc, 4);
4313 add_arg(mk_id(DESCRG(temp_sptr)));
4314 add_arg(check_member(arr_ast, mk_id(DESCRG(arr_sptr))));
4315 add_arg(dim);
4316 add_arg(ncopies);
4317 add_stmt_before(astStmt, arg_gbl.std);
4318}
4319
4320/** \brief Make a temporary to be used as the argument to an intrinsic that
4321 returns an array.
4322 \param func_ast ast for the intrinsic call
4323 \param func_args rewritten args for the function
4324 \param subscr returned subscripts
4325 \param elem_dty data type of elements
4326 \param lhs passed lhs or zero
4327 \param retval returned ast for lhs
4328
4329 The actual size of this temp is derived from the
4330 arguments to the intrinsic. The subscripts of the temp may not
4331 be the entire temp; this is derived from the arguments as well.
4332
4333 If lhs is non-zero, check lhs to see if it is OK for the intended
4334 use; if so, return 0.
4335 */
4336static int
4337mk_result_sptr(int func_ast, int func_args, int *subscr, int elem_dty, int lhs,
4338 int *retval)
4339{
4340 int temp_sptr = 0;
4341 int dim;
4342 int shape;
4343 int shape1;
4344 int rank, rank1;
4345 int arg;
4346 int ncopies;
4347
4348 shape = A_SHAPEG(func_ast);
4349 switch (A_OPTYPEG(func_ast)) {
4350 case I_MINLOC:
4351 case I_MAXLOC:
4352 case I_FINDLOC:
4353 case I_ALL:
4354 case I_ANY:
4355 case I_COUNT:
4356 case I_MAXVAL:
4357 case I_MINVAL:
4358 case I_PRODUCT:
4359 case I_SUM:
4360 case I_NORM2:
4361 arg = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
4362 /* first arg with dimension removed */
4363 dim = A_OPTYPEG(func_ast) == I_FINDLOC ? ARGT_ARG(func_args, 2)
4364 : ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
4365 assert(dim != 0, "mk_result_sptr: dim must be constant", 0, 4);
4366 /* We know that the first argument is an array section or whole
4367 * array, so we can squeeze out the dimension & just use the
4368 * existing subscripts.
4369 */
4370 temp_sptr = chk_reduc_sptr(arg, "r", subscr, elem_dty, dim, lhs, retval);
4371 /* non-constant DIM */
4372 if (!A_ALIASG(dim) && temp_sptr && A_SHAPEG(arg)) {
4373 int array, arrayast;
4374 array = find_array(arg, &arrayast);
4375 add_reduce_descriptor(temp_sptr, array, arrayast, dim);
4376 }
4377
4378 /* make the subscripts for the result */
4379 break;
4380 case I_UNPACK:
4381 /* mask (second arg) */
4382 arg = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
4383 goto easy;
4384 case I_CSHIFT:
4385 case I_EOSHIFT:
4386 arg = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
4387 while (A_TYPEG(arg) == A_INTR &&
4388 (A_OPTYPEG(arg) == I_CSHIFT || A_OPTYPEG(arg) == I_EOSHIFT)) {
4389 int fargs = A_ARGSG(arg);
4390 arg = ARGT_ARG(fargs, 0);
4391 }
4392 if (lhs == 0)
4393 goto easy;
4394 rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
4395 if (arg_gbl.lhs) {
4396 shape1 = A_SHAPEG(arg_gbl.lhs);
4397 rank1 = SHD_NDIM(shape1);
4398 if (rank == rank1 && !arg_gbl.used &&
4399 DTY(A_DTYPEG(arg_gbl.lhs) + 1) == elem_dty) {
4400 *retval = arg_gbl.lhs;
4401 temp_sptr = 0;
4402 arg_gbl.used = TRUE;
4403 break;
4404 }
4405 if (rank == rank1) {
4406 temp_sptr =
4407 chk_assign_sptr(arg_gbl.lhs, "r", subscr, elem_dty, lhs, retval);
4408 break;
4409 }
4410 }
4411 goto easy;
4412
4413 easy:
4414 if (ast_has_allocatable_member(lhs)) {
4415 goto temp_from_shape;
4416 }
4417 temp_sptr = chk_assign_sptr(arg, "r", subscr, elem_dty, lhs, retval);
4418 break;
4419 case I_SPREAD:
4420 /* first arg with dimension added */
4421 arg = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
4422 dim = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
4423 ncopies = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 2);
4424 assert(dim != 0, "mk_result_sptr: dim must be constant", 0, 4);
4425
4426 temp_sptr =
4427 mk_spread_sptr(arg, "r", subscr, elem_dty, dim, ncopies, lhs, retval);
4428 /* non-constant DIM */
4429 if (!A_ALIASG(dim) && temp_sptr && A_SHAPEG(arg)) {
4430 int array, arrayast;
4431 array = find_array(arg, &arrayast);
4432 add_spread_descriptor(temp_sptr, array, arrayast, dim, ncopies);
4433 }
4434
4435 break;
4436 case I_MATMUL:
4437 case I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE:
4438 rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
4439 if (matmul_use_lhs(lhs, rank, elem_dty)) {
4440 *retval = arg_gbl.lhs;
4441 temp_sptr = 0;
4442 arg_gbl.used = TRUE;
4443 break;
4444 }
4445 if (A_OPTYPEG(func_ast) == I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE) {
4446 /* NOTE: this assumes that I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE is
4447 * generated for the transpose of the first arg only
4448 */
4449 int tmp_shape = A_SHAPEG(ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0));
4450 arg = mk_id(mk_shape_sptr(tmp_shape, subscr, elem_dty));
4451 arg = mk_id(mk_transpose_sptr(arg, "r", subscr, elem_dty, retval));
4452 } else {
4453 arg = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
4454 }
4455
4456 /* first and second args */
4457 temp_sptr = mk_matmul_sptr(arg, ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1), "r", subscr,
4458 elem_dty, retval);
4459 break;
4460 case I_TRANSPOSE:
4461 /* first arg */
4462 goto temp_from_shape;
4463 case I_PACK:
4464 /* problem */
4465 /* just make a 1-d temp with the appropriate size and no dist */
4466 temp_sptr = mk_pack_sptr(shape, elem_dty);
4467 subscr[0] = mk_triple(SHD_LWB(shape, 0), SHD_UPB(shape, 0), 0);
4468 *retval = mk_id(temp_sptr);
4469 break;
4470 case I_RESHAPE:
4471 case I_TRANSFER:
4472 temp_from_shape:
4473 /* make a temp out of the shape, no distribution */
4474 temp_sptr = mk_shape_sptr(shape, subscr, elem_dty);
4475 *retval = mk_id(temp_sptr);
4476 break;
4477 default:
4478 interr("mk_result_sptr: can't handle intrinsic", func_ast, 4);
4479 break;
4480 }
4481 return temp_sptr;
4482}
4483
4484static LOGICAL
4485matmul_use_lhs(int lhs, int rank, int elem_dty)
4486{
4487 if (lhs && arg_gbl.lhs) {
4488 /*
4489 * the LHS cannot be a member whose shape comes froms a parent
4490 */
4491 int array;
4492 if (A_TYPEG(arg_gbl.lhs) == A_MEM && A_SHAPEG(A_PARENTG(arg_gbl.lhs)) != 0)
4493 return FALSE;
4494 /*
4495 * the LHS cannot be an allocatable if -Mallocatable=03 is enabled
4496 */
4497 array = find_array(arg_gbl.lhs, NULL);
4498 if (XBIT(54, 0x1) && ALLOCATTRG(array))
4499 return FALSE;
4500 if (rank == SHD_NDIM(A_SHAPEG(arg_gbl.lhs)) && arg_gbl.used == 0 &&
4501 DTY(A_DTYPEG(arg_gbl.lhs) + 1) == elem_dty) {
4502 return TRUE;
4503 }
4504 }
4505 return FALSE;
4506}
4507
4508int
4509search_conform_array(int ast, int flag)
4510{
4511 int i;
4512 int argt;
4513 int nargs;
4514 int j;
4515
4516 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
4517 case A_SUBSCR:
4518 if (A_SHAPEG(ast) != 0 && flag &&
4519 (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(ast)) == A_ID || A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(ast)) == A_MEM))
4520 return ast;
4521 return 0;
4522 case A_SUBSTR:
4523 return search_conform_array(A_LOPG(ast), flag);
4524 case A_ID:
4525 if (A_SHAPEG(ast))
4526 return ast;
4527 return 0;
4528 case A_BINOP:
4529 i = search_conform_array(A_LOPG(ast), flag);
4530 if (i != 0)
4531 return i;
4532 return search_conform_array(A_ROPG(ast), flag);
4533 case A_UNOP:
4534 case A_CONV:
4535 return search_conform_array(A_LOPG(ast), flag);
4536 case A_MEM:
4537 if (A_SHAPEG(A_MEMG(ast)))
4538 return ast;
4539 return search_conform_array(A_PARENTG(ast), flag);
4540 case A_INTR:
4541 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
4542 nargs = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
4543 if (INKINDG(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast))) != IK_ELEMENTAL) {
4544 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
4545 case I_CSHIFT:
4546 case I_EOSHIFT:
4547 return search_conform_array(ARGT_ARG(argt, 0), flag);
4548 case I_SPREAD:
4549 case I_SUM:
4550 case I_PRODUCT:
4551 case I_MAXVAL:
4552 case I_MINVAL:
4553 case I_DOT_PRODUCT:
4554 case I_ALL:
4555 case I_ANY:
4556 case I_COUNT:
4557 return ast;
4558 case I_TRANSPOSE:
4559 return ast;
4560 default:
4561 return 0;
4562 }
4563 }
4564 for (i = 0; i < nargs; ++i)
4565 if (A_SHAPEG(ARGT_ARG(argt, i)))
4566 if ((j = search_conform_array(ARGT_ARG(argt, i), flag)) != 0)
4567 return j;
4568 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
4569 case A_FUNC:
4570 if (elemental_func_call(ast)) {
4571 /* search up to all arguments of elemental function for
4572 * a conformable array -- not just the first argument.
4573 */
4574 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
4575 nargs = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
4576 for (i = 0; i < nargs; ++i) {
4577 if ((j = search_conform_array(ARGT_ARG(argt, i), flag)))
4578 return j;
4579 }
4580 }
4581 return 0;
4582 default:
4583 return 0;
4584 }
4585}
4586
4587/* Pointer association status (logical function):
4588 * associated(pv [, target] )
4589 * external pghpf_associated
4590 * logical pghpf_associated
4591 * ( pghpf_associated(pv, pv$sdsc, target, target$d) )
4592 */
4593static int
4594transform_associated(int std, int ast)
4595{
4596 int ast1;
4597 int argt, nargs;
4598 int pv, arr;
4599 int pv_sptr = 0, arr_sptr;
4600 int arr_desc, static_desc;
4601 int dtype;
4602 int func;
4603 int ty;
4604 int with_target;
4605
4606 assert(A_TYPEG(ast) == A_INTR && A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_ASSOCIATED,
4607 "transform_associated: not ASSOCIATED call", 2, ast);
4608
4609 with_target = 0;
4610 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
4611 nargs = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
4612 assert(nargs == 2,
4613 "transform_associated: ASSOCIATED with wrong number arguments", 2,
4614 ast);
4615 pv = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
4616 arr = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
4617 arr_desc = 0;
4618 assert(A_TYPEG(pv) == A_ID || A_TYPEG(pv) == A_MEM,
4619 "transform_associated: ASSOCIATED(V) where V is not an ID", 2, ast);
4620 if (A_TYPEG(pv) == A_ID) {
4621 pv_sptr = A_SPTRG(pv);
4622 } else if (A_TYPEG(pv) == A_MEM) {
4623 pv_sptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(pv));
4624 }
4625 dtype = DTYPEG(pv_sptr);
4626 DESCUSEDP(pv_sptr, 1);
4627
4628 arr_sptr = 0;
4629 if (arr) {
4630 switch (A_TYPEG(arr)) {
4631 case A_SUBSCR:
4632 case A_MEM:
4633 case A_ID:
4634 arr_sptr = memsym_of_ast(arr);
4635 break;
4636 default:
4637 assert(0, "transform_associated: ASSOCIATED(V,P) where P is not an ID", 2,
4638 ast);
4639 }
4640 }
4641
4642 if (!arr)
4643 return ast;
4644 /* if this is an undistributed scalar pointer,
4645 * and there is no array 2nd argument, leave this as it is */
4646 if (DTY(dtype) != TY_ARRAY) {
4647 /* 2nd argument must also be scalar */
4648 switch (A_TYPEG(arr)) {
4649 case A_ID:
4650 case A_MEM:
4651 /* must not be an array */
4652 if (DTY(DTYPEG(arr_sptr)) != TY_ARRAY)
4653 return ast;
4654 break;
4655 }
4656 }
4657
4658 if (arr) {
4659 with_target = 1;
4660 DESCUSEDP(arr_sptr, 1);
4661 if (A_SHAPEG(arr) && A_TYPEG(arr) == A_SUBSCR) {
4662 arr_desc = mk_id(make_sec_from_ast(arr, std, std, 0, 0));
4663 arr = A_LOPG(arr);
4664 } else if (A_SHAPEG(arr) && (A_TYPEG(arr) == A_ID || A_TYPEG(arr) == A_MEM))
4665 arr_desc = mk_id(DESCRG(arr_sptr));
4666 else {
4667 ty = dtype_to_arg(A_DTYPEG(arr));
4668 arr_desc = mk_isz_cval(ty, astb.bnd.dtype);
4669 }
4670 } else {
4671 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_CHAR)
4672 arr = astb.ptr0c;
4673 else
4674 arr = astb.ptr0;
4675 arr_desc = astb.bnd.one;
4676 }
4677 assert(arr_desc, "transform_associated: need descriptor", 2, arr);
4678
4679 if (!POINTERG(pv_sptr))
4680 error(506, 3, STD_LINENO(std), SYMNAME(pv_sptr), CNULL);
4681 static_desc = mk_id(SDSCG(pv_sptr));
4682
4683 nargs = 4;
4684 if (XBIT(70, 0x20)) {
4685 if (MIDNUMG(pv_sptr))
4686 ++nargs;
4687 if (PTROFFG(pv_sptr))
4688 ++nargs;
4689 }
4690 argt = mk_argt(nargs);
4691 ARGT_ARG(argt, 0) = pv;
4692 ARGT_ARG(argt, 1) = check_member(pv, static_desc);
4693 ARGT_ARG(argt, 2) = arr;
4694 ARGT_ARG(argt, 3) = check_member(arr, arr_desc);
4695 nargs = 4;
4696 if (XBIT(70, 0x20)) {
4697 if (MIDNUMG(pv_sptr)) {
4698 ARGT_ARG(argt, nargs) = check_member(pv, mk_id(MIDNUMG(pv_sptr)));
4699 ++nargs;
4700 }
4701 if (PTROFFG(pv_sptr)) {
4702 ARGT_ARG(argt, nargs) = check_member(pv, mk_id(PTROFFG(pv_sptr)));
4703 ++nargs;
4704 }
4705 }
4706
4707 if (with_target) {
4708 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_CHAR)
4709 func = mk_id(sym_mkfunc(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_associated_tchara), DT_LOG));
4710 else
4711 func = mk_id(sym_mkfunc(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_associated_t), DT_LOG));
4712 } else {
4713 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_CHAR)
4714 func = mk_id(sym_mkfunc(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_associated_chara), DT_LOG));
4715 else
4716 func = mk_id(sym_mkfunc(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_associated), DT_LOG));
4717 }
4718
4719 ast1 = mk_func_node(A_FUNC, func, nargs, argt);
4720
4721 NODESCP(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast1)), 1);
4722 A_DTYPEP(ast1, DT_LOG);
4723 return ast1;
4724}
4725
4726/* func_ast: A_FUNC or A_INTR */
4727/* func_args: rewritten args */
4728static void
4729transform_mvbits(int func_ast, int func_args)
4730{
4731 int lb, ub, st;
4732 int forall, dovar;
4733 int ast;
4734 int lineno;
4735 int stdnext, std;
4736 int newast;
4737 int to;
4738 int shape;
4739 int i, n;
4740 int triplet_list, index_var;
4741 int triplet;
4742 int newargt;
4743 int nargs;
4744
4745 assert(A_TYPEG(func_ast) == A_ICALL && A_OPTYPEG(func_ast) == I_MVBITS,
4746 "transform_mvbits: something is wrong", 2, func_ast);
4747
4748 stdnext = arg_gbl.std;
4749 lineno = STD_LINENO(stdnext);
4750
4751 to = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 3);
4752 shape = A_SHAPEG(to);
4753 if (!shape) {
4754 return;
4755 }
4756
4757 forall = make_forall(shape, to, 0, 0);
4758
4759 n = 0;
4760 triplet_list = A_LISTG(forall);
4761 for (; triplet_list; triplet_list = ASTLI_NEXT(triplet_list)) {
4762 n++;
4763 newast = mk_stmt(A_DO, 0);
4764 index_var = ASTLI_SPTR(triplet_list);
4765 triplet = ASTLI_TRIPLE(triplet_list);
4766 dovar = mk_id(index_var);
4767 A_DOVARP(newast, dovar);
4768 lb = A_LBDG(triplet);
4769 ub = A_UPBDG(triplet);
4770 st = A_STRIDEG(triplet);
4771
4772 A_M1P(newast, lb);
4773 A_M2P(newast, ub);
4774 A_M3P(newast, st);
4775 A_M4P(newast, 0);
4776
4777 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
4778 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
4779 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
4780 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
4781 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
4782 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
4783 }
4784
4785 nargs = 5;
4786 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
4787
4788 for (i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
4789 ast = ARGT_ARG(func_args, i);
4790 ast = normalize_forall(forall, ast, 0);
4791 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = ast;
4792 }
4793
4794 newast = mk_func_node(A_ICALL, A_LOPG(func_ast), nargs, newargt);
4795 A_OPTYPEP(newast, A_OPTYPEG(func_ast));
4796 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
4797 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
4798 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
4799 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
4800 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
4801 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
4802
4803 for (i = 0; i < n; i++) {
4804 newast = mk_stmt(A_ENDDO, 0);
4805 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
4806 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
4807 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
4808 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
4809 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
4810 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
4811 }
4812 delete_stmt(arg_gbl.std);
4813}

4817static void
4818transform_merge(int func_ast, int func_args)
4819{

4833

4836

4838 lineno = STD_LINENO(stdnext);
4839
4840 temp = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);

4865 A_M4P(newast, 0);

4871 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
4872 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
4873 }
4874
4875 nargs = ARGT_CNT(func_args);
4876 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
4877
4878 for (i = 0; i < nargs; i++) {
4879 ast = ARGT_ARG(func_args, i);
4880 ast = normalize_forall(forall, ast, 0);
4881 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = ast;
4882 }
4883
4884 newast = mk_func_node(A_CALL, A_LOPG(func_ast), nargs, newargt);
4885 A_OPTYPEP(newast, A_OPTYPEG(func_ast));
4886 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
4887 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
4888 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
4889 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
4890 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
4891 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
4892
4893 for (i = 0; i < n; i++) {
4894 newast = mk_stmt(A_ENDDO, 0);
4895 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
4896 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
4897 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
4898 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
4899 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
4900 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);

4902 delete_stmt(arg_gbl.std);

4905static void
4906transform_elemental(int func_ast, int func_args)
4907{
4908 int lb, ub, st;
4909 int forall, dovar;
4910 int ast;
4911 int lineno;
4912 int stdnext, std;
4913 int newast;
4914 int temp;
4915 int shape;
4916 int i, n;
4917 int triplet_list, index_var;
4918 int triplet;
4919 int newargt;
4920 int nargs;
4921
4922 assert(A_TYPEG(func_ast) == A_CALL && elemental_func_call(func_ast),
4923 "transform_merge: something is wrong", func_ast, 3);
4924
4925 stdnext = arg_gbl.std;
4926 lineno = STD_LINENO(stdnext);
4927
4928 temp = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
4929 shape = extract_shape_from_args(func_ast);
4930 if (!shape) {
4931 A_TYPEP(func_ast, A_CALL);
4932 return;
4933 }
4934
4935 forall = make_forall(shape, temp, 0, 0);
4936
4937 n = 0;
4938 triplet_list = A_LISTG(forall);
4939 for (; triplet_list; triplet_list = ASTLI_NEXT(triplet_list)) {
4940 n++;
4941 newast = mk_stmt(A_DO, 0);
4942 index_var = ASTLI_SPTR(triplet_list);
4943 triplet = ASTLI_TRIPLE(triplet_list);
4944 dovar = mk_id(index_var);
4945 A_DOVARP(newast, dovar);
4946 lb = A_LBDG(triplet);
4947 ub = A_UPBDG(triplet);
4948 st = A_STRIDEG(triplet);
4949
4950 A_M1P(newast, lb);
4951 A_M2P(newast, ub);
4952 A_M3P(newast, st);
4953 A_M4P(newast, 0);
4954
4955 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
4956 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
4957 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
4958 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
4959 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
4960 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
4961 }
4962
4963 nargs = ARGT_CNT(func_args);
4964 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
4965
4966 for (i = 0; i < nargs; i++) {
4967 ast = ARGT_ARG(func_args, i);
4968 ast = normalize_forall(forall, ast, 0);
4969 ARGT_ARG(newargt, i) = ast;
4970 }
4971
4972 newast = mk_func_node(A_CALL, A_LOPG(func_ast), nargs, newargt);
4973 A_OPTYPEP(newast, A_OPTYPEG(func_ast));
4974 A_INVOKING_DESCP(newast, A_INVOKING_DESCG(func_ast));
4975 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
4976 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
4977 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
4978 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
4979 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
4980 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
