4982 for (i = 0; i < n; i++) {
4983 newast = mk_stmt(A_ENDDO, 0);
4984 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
4985 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
4986 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
4987 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
4988 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
4989 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
4990 }
4991 delete_stmt(arg_gbl.std);
4992}
4993
4994/* move_alloc(from, to) */
4995static void
4996transform_move_alloc(int func_ast, int func_args)
4997{
4998 int std;
4999 int pvar, pvar2;
5000 int desc, desc2;
5001 SPTR sptr, sptr2;
5002 int func, nargs, newast, newargt;
5003 int stdnext = arg_gbl.std;
5004 int lineno = STD_LINENO(stdnext);
5005 int fptr = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
5006 int fptr2 = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
5007
5008 move_alloc_arg(fptr, &sptr, &pvar);
5009 move_alloc_arg(fptr2, &sptr2, &pvar2);
5010
5011 desc = find_descriptor_ast(sptr, fptr);
5012 assert(desc, "transform_move_alloc: invalid 'from' descriptor", sptr,
5013 ERR_Fatal);
5014 desc2 = find_descriptor_ast(sptr2, fptr2);
5015 assert(desc2, "transform_move_alloc: invalid 'to' descriptor", sptr2,
5016 ERR_Fatal);
5017
5018 func = mk_id(sym_mkfunc_nodesc_expst(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_move_alloc), DT_INT));
5019 nargs = 4;
5020 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
5021 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = pvar; /* from ptr */
5022 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = desc; /* from descriptor */
5023 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 2) = pvar2; /* to ptr */
5024 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 3) = desc2; /* to descriptor */
5025 newast = mk_func_node(A_CALL, func, nargs, newargt);
5026 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
5027
5028 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
5029 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
5030 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
5031 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
5032 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
5033 if (A_SHAPEG(fptr2) && sptr != sptr2 && !SDSCG(sptr2)) {
5034 int parent = STYPEG(sptr) == ST_MEMBER ? A_PARENTG(fptr) : 0;
5035 int parent2 = STYPEG(sptr2) == ST_MEMBER ? A_PARENTG(fptr2) : 0;
5036 copy_surrogate_to_bnds_vars(DTYPEG(sptr2), parent2, DTYPEG(sptr), parent,
5037 STD_NEXT(std));
5038 }
5039
5040 delete_stmt(arg_gbl.std);
5041}
5042
5043static void
5044transform_c_f_pointer(int func_ast, int func_args)
5045{
5046 /*
5047 * c_f_pointer(cptr, fptr) -- fptr is scalar
5048 * c_f_pointer(cptr, fptr, shape) -- fptr is array
5049 */
5050 int lineno;
5051 int stdnext, std;
5052 int newast;
5053 int rank;
5054 int fptr;
5055 int cptr, newcptrarg;
5056 int pvar = 0;
5057 int shape;
5058 int desc;
5059 int fty;
5060 int dtype;
5061 int func;
5062 int nargs;
5063 int newargt;
5064 int sptr;
5065 int shpty;
5066 int sz;
5067
5068 stdnext = arg_gbl.std;
5069 lineno = STD_LINENO(stdnext);
5070 fptr = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
5071 cptr = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
5072 /*
5073 * pass the address of fptr$p instead of just referencing fptr.
5074 */
5075 dtype = A_DTYPEG(fptr);
5076 if (A_TYPEG(fptr) == A_ID)
5077 sptr = A_SPTRG(fptr);
5078 else if (A_TYPEG(fptr) == A_MEM)
5079 sptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(fptr));
5080 else
5081 sptr = 0;
5082 if (sptr && MIDNUMG(sptr)) {
5083 pvar = check_member(fptr, mk_id(MIDNUMG(sptr)));
5084 } else {
5085 interr("FPTR error in c_f_pointer()", fptr, 4);
5086 }
5087
5088 /* if argument:cptr does not have type(c_ptr), create a temporary
5089 * and assign its location to that temp. Pass that temp to
5090 * c_f_pointer.
5091 */
5092 if (!is_iso_c_ptr(A_DTYPEG(cptr)) && !is_cuf_c_devptr(A_DTYPEG(cptr))) {
5093 DTYPE dt = get_iso_c_ptr();
5094 if (dt <= DT_NONE)
5095 interr("Error in c_f_pointer() - unable to find c_ptr type", fptr, 4);
5096 newcptrarg = mk_id(get_temp(dt));
5097 cptr = mk_unop(OP_LOC, cptr, DT_PTR);
5098 cptr = mk_assn_stmt(newcptrarg, cptr, dt);
5099 add_stmt_before(cptr, arg_gbl.std);
5100 cptr = newcptrarg;
5101 }
5102
5103 shape = A_SHAPEG(fptr);
5104 if (!shape) { /* scalar */
5105 rank = 0;
5106 desc = astb.i0;
5107 shape = astb.i0;
5108 shpty = astb.i0;
5109 } else {
5110 /*
5111 * pass the address of fptr$sd
5112 */
5113 rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
5114 if (SDSCG(sptr)) {
5115 desc = check_member(fptr, mk_id(SDSCG(sptr)));
5116 DESCUSEDP(sptr, 1);
5117 NODESCP(sptr, 0);
5118 } else {
5119 desc = check_member(fptr, mk_id(DESCRG(sptr)));
5120 DESCUSEDP(sptr, 1);
5121 NODESCP(sptr, 0);
5122 }
5123 shape = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 2);
5124 shpty = dtype_to_arg(DTY(A_DTYPEG(shape) + 1));
5125 shpty = mk_cval(shpty, astb.bnd.dtype);
5126 }
5127
5128 dtype = DDTG(dtype);
5129 fty = dtype_to_arg(dtype);
5130 fty = mk_cval(fty, astb.bnd.dtype);
5131 switch (DTY(dtype)) {
5132 case TY_CHAR:
5133 case TY_NCHAR:
5134 sz = ast_intr(I_LEN, astb.bnd.dtype, 1, fptr);
5135 break;
5136 default:
5137 sz = mk_cval(size_of(dtype), astb.bnd.dtype);
5138 break;
5139 }
5140 func = mk_id(sym_mkfunc_nodesc_expst(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_c_f_ptr), DT_INT));
5141
5142 nargs = 8;
5143 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
5144 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = cptr; /* cptr */
5145 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = mk_cval(rank, astb.bnd.dtype); /* rank */
5146 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 2) = sz; /* len/size of fptr */
5147 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 3) = pvar; /* fptr$p */
5148 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 4) = desc; /* fptr$sd */
5149 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 5) = fty; /* eltype of fptr */
5150 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 6) = shape; /* shape */
5151 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 7) = shpty; /* eltype of shape */
5152 newast = mk_func_node(A_CALL, func, nargs, newargt);
5153 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
5154 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
5155 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
5156 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
5157 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
5158 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
5159 delete_stmt(arg_gbl.std);
5160}
5161
5162static void
5163transform_c_f_procpointer(int func_ast, int func_args)
5164{
5165 /*
5166 * c_f_procpointer(cptr, fptr)
5167 * call RTE_c_f_procptr, passing the address of cptr and fptr$p.
5168 * lower() could turn this into an assignment of the form:
5169 * fptr$p = cptr%val
5170 * But today, I do not want to deal with assigning an integer (cptr%val)
5171 * to a pointer variable.
5172 */
5173 int lineno;
5174 int stdnext, std;
5175 int newast;
5176 int fptr;
5177 int pvar = 0;
5178 int dtype;
5179 int func;
5180 int nargs;
5181 int newargt;
5182 int sptr;
5183
5184 stdnext = arg_gbl.std;
5185 lineno = STD_LINENO(stdnext);
5186 fptr = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
5187 /*
5188 * pass the address of fptr$p instead of just referencing fptr.
5189 */
5190 dtype = A_DTYPEG(fptr);
5191 if (A_TYPEG(fptr) == A_ID)
5192 sptr = A_SPTRG(fptr);
5193 else if (A_TYPEG(fptr) == A_MEM)
5194 sptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(fptr));
5195 else
5196 sptr = 0;
5197 if (sptr && MIDNUMG(sptr)) {
5198 pvar = check_member(fptr, mk_id(MIDNUMG(sptr)));
5199 } else {
5200 interr("FPTR error in c_f_procpointer()", fptr, 4);
5201 }
5202
5203 func = mk_id(sym_mkfunc_nodesc_expst(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_c_f_procptr), DT_INT));
5204 nargs = 2;
5205 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
5206 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0); /* cptr */
5207 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = pvar; /* fptr$p */
5208 newast = mk_func_node(A_CALL, func, nargs, newargt);
5209 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
5210 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
5211 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
5212 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
5213 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
5214 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
5215 delete_stmt(arg_gbl.std);
5216}
5217
5218static void
5219_rewrite_scalar_fuctions(int astx, int *std)
5220{
5221 int sptrretval;
5222 int sptrtmp;
5223 int funcsptr;
5224 int iface;
5225 int ast;
5226 int asttmp;
5227 int args;
5228
5229 if (A_TYPEG(astx) == A_FUNC && DT_ISSCALAR(A_DTYPEG(astx))) {
5230 funcsptr = procsym_of_ast(A_LOPG(astx));
5231 proc_arginfo(funcsptr, NULL, NULL, &iface);
5232 if (iface && FVALG(iface)) {
5233 args = rewrite_sub_args(astx, 0);
5234 A_ARGSP(astx, args);
5235 sptrretval = FVALG(iface);
5236 sptrtmp = sym_get_scalar(SYMNAME(sptrretval), "r", A_DTYPEG(astx));
5237 asttmp = mk_id(sptrtmp);
5238 ast = mk_assn_stmt(asttmp, astx, A_DTYPEG(astx));
5239 add_stmt_before(ast, *std);
5240 ast_replace(astx, asttmp);
5241 }
5242 }
5243}
5244
5245static int
5246rewrite_scalar_functions(int astx, int std)
5247{
5248 int ast;
5249
5250 ast_visit(1, 1);
5251 ast_traverse(astx, NULL, _rewrite_scalar_fuctions, &std);
5252 ast = ast_rewrite(astx);
5253 ast_unvisit();
5254 return ast;
5255}
5256
5257/*
5258 * Return TRUE if AST astx contains an intrinsic or external call.
5259 * allow calls to user or intrinsic elementals
5260 */
5261static LOGICAL
5262_contains_any_call(int astx, LOGICAL *pflag)
5263{
5264 if (A_TYPEG(astx) == A_INTR) {
5265 /* allow elemental intrinsic call s*/
5266 if (INKINDG(procsym_of_ast(A_LOPG(astx))) == IK_ELEMENTAL) {
5267 return FALSE;
5268 }
5269 *pflag = TRUE;
5270 return TRUE;
5271 } else if (A_TYPEG(astx) == A_CALL || A_TYPEG(astx) == A_FUNC) {
5272 if (elemental_func_call(astx)) {
5273 return FALSE;
5274 }
5275 *pflag = TRUE;
5276 return TRUE;
5277
5278 } else if (A_TYPEG(astx) == A_ICALL) {
5279 *pflag = TRUE;
5280 return TRUE;
5281 }
5282 return FALSE;
5283}
5284
5285/*
5286 * Return TRUE if AST astx contains an intrinsic or external call.
5287 * allow calls to user or intrinsic elementals
5288 */
5289static LOGICAL
5290contains_any_call(int astx)
5291{
5292 LOGICAL flag = FALSE;
5293 ast_visit(1, 1);
5294 ast_traverse(astx, _contains_any_call, NULL, &flag);
5295 ast_unvisit();
5296 return flag;
5297}
5298
5299static int subscript_lhs(int, int *, int, DTYPE, int, int);
5300
5301static LOGICAL
5302ast_cval(int ast, ISZ_T *value)
5303{
5304 if (ast && A_ALIASG(ast))
5305 ast = A_ALIASG(ast);
5306 if (ast && A_TYPEG(ast) == A_CNST) {
5307 int sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
5308 if (sptr && STYPEG(sptr) == ST_CONST) {
5309 *value = get_isz_cval(sptr);
5310 return TRUE;
5311 }
5312 }
5313 return FALSE;
5314} /* ast_cval */
5315
5316/*
5317 * from a(1:3:1,2:4:2) given offsets 'i' and 'j' for subscripts 'si' and 'sj',
5318 * build the reference a(1+i, 2+j*2) and return that
5319 * This routine does the array reference rewrite
5320 */
5321static int
5322build_array_reference(int ast, int si, int vi, int sj, int vj)
5323{
5324 int asd, numdim, k, ss, iss;
5325 int subs[MAXSUBS];
5326 asd = A_ASDG(ast);
5327 numdim = ASD_NDIM(asd);
5328 iss = 0;
5329 for (k = 0; k < numdim; ++k) {
5330 ss = ASD_SUBS(asd, k);
5331 if (A_TYPEG(ss) == A_TRIPLE) {
5332 int v, a;
5333 if (iss == si) {
5334 v = vi;
5335 } else if (iss == sj) {
5336 v = vj;
5337 } else {
5338 return 0;
5339 }
5340 /* return A_LBDG(ss) + A_STRIDEG(ss) * v */
5341 a = mk_cval(v, A_DTYPEG(A_STRIDEG(ss)));
5342 a = mk_binop(OP_MUL, a, A_STRIDEG(ss), A_DTYPEG(A_STRIDEG(ss)));
5343 a = mk_binop(OP_ADD, a, A_LBDG(ss), A_DTYPEG(A_LBDG(ss)));
5344 subs[k] = a;
5345 ++iss;
5346 } else if (A_SHAPEG(ss)) {
5347 return 0;
5348 } else {
5349 subs[k] = ss;
5350 }
5351 }
5352 ast = mk_subscr(A_LOPG(ast), subs, numdim, DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast)));
5353 return ast;
5354} /* build_array_reference */
5355
5356/*
5357 * from a(1:3:1,2:4:2) given offsets 'i' and 'j' for subscripts 'si' and 'sj',
5358 * build the reference a(1+i, 2+j*2) and return that
5359 * This routine walks the expression tree to find the array reference(s)
5360 */
5361static int
5362build_array_ref(int inast, int si, int vi, int sj, int vj)
5363{
5364 int ast1, ast2, dtype, args, arg1;
5365 int shape, argt, nargs, k;
5366 switch (A_TYPEG(inast)) {
5367 case A_BINOP:
5368 ast1 = build_array_ref(A_LOPG(inast), si, vi, sj, vj);
5369 if (ast1 == 0)
5370 return 0;
5371 ast2 = build_array_ref(A_ROPG(inast), si, vi, sj, vj);
5372 if (ast2 == 0)
5373 return 0;
5374 dtype = A_DTYPEG(inast);
5375 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY)
5376 dtype = DTY(dtype + 1);
5377 return mk_binop(A_OPTYPEG(inast), ast1, ast2, dtype);
5378 case A_UNOP:
5379 ast1 = build_array_ref(A_LOPG(inast), si, vi, sj, vj);
5380 if (ast1 == 0)
5381 return 0;
5382 dtype = A_DTYPEG(inast);
5383 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY)
5384 dtype = DTY(dtype + 1);
5385 return mk_unop(A_OPTYPEG(inast), ast1, dtype);
5386 case A_CONV:
5387 ast1 = build_array_ref(A_LOPG(inast), si, vi, sj, vj);
5388 if (ast1 == 0)
5389 return 0;
5390 dtype = A_DTYPEG(inast);
5391 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY)
5392 dtype = DTY(dtype + 1);
5393 return mk_convert(ast1, dtype);
5394 case A_CMPLXC:
5395 case A_CNST:
5396 return inast;
5397 case A_SUBSTR:
5398 ast1 = build_array_ref(A_LOPG(inast), si, vi, sj, vj);
5399 if (ast1 == 0)
5400 return 0;
5401 return mk_substr(ast1, A_LEFTG(inast), A_RIGHTG(inast), A_DTYPEG(inast));
5402 case A_PAREN:
5403 ast1 = build_array_ref(A_LOPG(inast), si, vi, sj, vj);
5404 if (ast1 == 0)
5405 return 0;
5406 return mk_paren(ast1, A_DTYPEG(ast1));
5407
5408 case A_FUNC:
5409 shape = A_SHAPEG(inast);
5410 if (shape) {
5411 argt = A_ARGSG(inast);
5412 nargs = A_ARGCNTG(inast);
5413 for (k = 0; k < nargs; ++k) {
5414 ast1 = build_array_ref(ARGT_ARG(argt, k), si, vi, sj, vj);
5415 if (ast1 == 0)
5416 return 0;
5417 }
5418 /* now for real */
5419 for (k = 0; k < nargs; ++k) {
5420 ARGT_ARG(argt, k) = build_array_ref(ARGT_ARG(argt, k), si, vi, sj, vj);
5421 }
5422 dtype = A_DTYPEG(inast);
5423 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY && elemental_func_call(inast)) {
5424 A_DTYPEP(inast, DTY(dtype + 1));
5425 A_SHAPEP(inast, 0);
5426 }
5427 }
5428 return inast;
5429 case A_SUBSCR:
5430 /* does this subscript have any triplet entries */
5431 if (vector_member(inast)) {
5432 inast = build_array_reference(inast, si, vi, sj, vj);
5433 }
5434 if (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(inast)) == A_MEM) {
5435 /* the parent might have an array index */
5436 int asd = A_ASDG(inast);
5437 ast1 = build_array_ref(A_PARENTG(A_LOPG(inast)), si, vi, sj, vj);
5438 if (ast1 == 0)
5439 return 0;
5440 if (ast1 != A_PARENTG(A_LOPG(inast))) {
5441 DTYPE dtype = A_DTYPEG(A_MEMG(A_LOPG(inast)));
5442 ast1 = mk_member(ast1, A_MEMG(A_LOPG(inast)), dtype);
5443 if (is_array_dtype(dtype))
5444 dtype = array_element_dtype(dtype);
5445 /* add the member subscripts */
5446 inast = mk_subscr_copy(ast1, asd, dtype);
5447 }
5448 }
5449 return inast;
5450 case A_MEM:
5451 /* the parent might have an array index */
5452 ast1 = build_array_ref(A_PARENTG(inast), si, vi, sj, vj);
5453 if (ast1 == 0)
5454 return 0;
5455 /* member should be a scalar here */
5456 return mk_member(ast1, A_MEMG(inast), A_DTYPEG(A_MEMG(inast)));
5457 case A_ID:
5458 return inast;
5459 case A_INTR:
5460 /* allow transpose() call */
5461 if (A_OPTYPEG(inast) != I_TRANSPOSE) {
5462 return 0;
5463 }
5464 args = A_ARGSG(inast);
5465 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(args, 0);
5466 ast1 = build_array_ref(arg1, sj, vi, si, vj);
5467 return ast1;
5468 default:
5469 return 0;
5470 }
5471
5472} /* build_array_ref */
5473
5474/*
5475 * a = matmul( b, c )
5476 * where the extent of a, b, c is less than 3 in each dimension
5477 * inline to
5478 * a(i,j) = sum(b(i,k) * c(k,j))
5479 * where we expand i, j, k at compile time from 1 to the extent.
5480 * for I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE, we transpose the first argument:
5481 * a(i,j) = sum(b(k,i) * c(k,j))
5482 * if dest is zero, we have to create a temp array of the appropriate size
5483 * and return a reference to that array.
5484 */
5485
5486static int
5487inline_small_matmul(int ast, int dest)
5488{
5489 ISZ_T ilow, ihigh, istride, iextent;
5490 ISZ_T jlow, jhigh, jstride, jextent;
5491 ISZ_T klow, khigh, kstride, kextent;
5492 ISZ_T klowx, khighx, kstridex, kextentx;
5493 int ii, kk;
5494 int args, arg1, arg2, array1, array2, arraydest;
5495 int shape1, shape2;
5496 int stdnext, lineno;
5497 int i, j, k;
5498 int mulop, addop;
5499 int stdprev;
5500 if (XBIT(47, 0x200))
5501 return ast;
5502 args = A_ARGSG(ast);
5503 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(args, 0);
5504 arg2 = ARGT_ARG(args, 1);
5505 if (!arg1 || !arg2)
5506 return ast;
5507
5508 stdprev = STD_PREV(arg_gbl.std);
5509 arg1 = rewrite_scalar_functions(arg1, arg_gbl.std);
5510 if (contains_any_call(arg1)) {
5511 arg1 = rewrite_sub_ast(arg1, 0);
5512 if (arg1 == -1)
5513 return ast;
5514 }
5515 arg2 = rewrite_scalar_functions(arg2, arg_gbl.std);
5516 if (contains_any_call(arg2)) {
5517 arg2 = rewrite_sub_ast(arg2, 0);
5518 if (arg2 == -1)
5519 return ast;
5520 }
5521 if (stdprev != STD_PREV(arg_gbl.std)) {
5522 /*
5523 * Allocatable temps could have been created while processing
5524 * the arguments and would degrade performance if we don't cleanup.
5525 * So, if any statements were created for the * arguments, just
5526 * make a new matmul ast
5527 */
5528 int argtnew, astnew;
5529 argtnew = mk_argt(2);
5530 ARGT_ARG(argtnew, 0) = arg1;
5531 ARGT_ARG(argtnew, 1) = arg2;
5532 astnew = mk_func_node(A_TYPEG(ast), A_LOPG(ast), 2, argtnew);
5533 A_OPTYPEP(astnew, A_OPTYPEG(ast));
5534 A_SHAPEP(astnew, A_SHAPEG(ast));
5535 A_DTYPEP(astnew, A_DTYPEG(ast));
5536 ast = astnew;
5537 }
5538 shape1 = A_SHAPEG(arg1);
5539 shape2 = A_SHAPEG(arg2);
5540 /* must be (n,k)x(k,m), or (k)x(k,m) or (n,k)x(k) */
5541 if (SHD_NDIM(shape1) != 2 && SHD_NDIM(shape1) != 1)
5542 return ast;
5543 if (SHD_NDIM(shape2) != 2 && SHD_NDIM(shape2) != 1)
5544 return ast;
5545 if (SHD_NDIM(shape1) == 1 && SHD_NDIM(shape2) == 1)
5546 return ast;
5547 /* check for transposed 1st argument */
5548 ii = 0;
5549 kk = 1;
5550 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE) {
5551 ii = 1;
5552 kk = 0;
5553 }
5554 /* the shapes must be constant sizes */
5555 if (SHD_NDIM(shape1) == 1) {
5556 ilow = 0;
5557 ihigh = 0;
5558 istride = 1;
5559 ii = 1;
5560 kk = 0;
5561 if (!ast_cval(SHD_LWB(shape1, kk), &klow))
5562 return ast;
5563 if (!ast_cval(SHD_UPB(shape1, kk), &khigh))
5564 return ast;
5565 if (!ast_cval(SHD_STRIDE(shape1, kk), &kstride))
5566 return ast;
5567 } else {
5568 if (!ast_cval(SHD_LWB(shape1, ii), &ilow))
5569 return ast;
5570 if (!ast_cval(SHD_UPB(shape1, ii), &ihigh))
5571 return ast;
5572 if (!ast_cval(SHD_STRIDE(shape1, ii), &istride))
5573 return ast;
5574 if (!ast_cval(SHD_LWB(shape1, kk), &klow))
5575 return ast;
5576 if (!ast_cval(SHD_UPB(shape1, kk), &khigh))
5577 return ast;
5578 if (!ast_cval(SHD_STRIDE(shape1, kk), &kstride))
5579 return ast;
5580 }
5581 if (SHD_NDIM(shape2) == 1) {
5582 jlow = 0;
5583 jhigh = 0;
5584 jstride = 1;
5585 if (!ast_cval(SHD_LWB(shape2, 0), &klowx))
5586 return ast;
5587 if (!ast_cval(SHD_UPB(shape2, 0), &khighx))
5588 return ast;
5589 if (!ast_cval(SHD_STRIDE(shape2, 0), &kstridex))
5590 return ast;
5591 } else {
5592 if (!ast_cval(SHD_LWB(shape2, 0), &klowx))
5593 return ast;
5594 if (!ast_cval(SHD_UPB(shape2, 0), &khighx))
5595 return ast;
5596 if (!ast_cval(SHD_STRIDE(shape2, 0), &kstridex))
5597 return ast;
5598 if (!ast_cval(SHD_LWB(shape2, 1), &jlow))
5599 return ast;
5600 if (!ast_cval(SHD_UPB(shape2, 1), &jhigh))
5601 return ast;
5602 if (!ast_cval(SHD_STRIDE(shape2, 1), &jstride))
5603 return ast;
5604 }
5605 if (istride == 0 || kstride == 0 || kstridex == 0 || jstride == 0)
5606 return ast;
5607 iextent = (ihigh - ilow + istride) / istride;
5608 jextent = (jhigh - jlow + jstride) / jstride;
5609 kextent = (khigh - klow + kstride) / kstride;
5610 kextentx = (khighx - klowx + kstridex) / kstridex;
5611 if (kextent != kextentx)
5612 return ast;
5613
5614 /* See if it's small enough */
5615 if (iextent <= 0 || iextent > 4)
5616 return ast;
5617 if (jextent <= 0 || jextent > 4)
5618 return ast;
5619 if (kextent <= 0 || kextent > 4)
5620 return ast;
5621 if (iextent * jextent * kextent > 32)
5622 return ast;
5623
5624 array1 = convert_subscript_in_expr(arg1);
5625 array2 = convert_subscript_in_expr(arg2);
5626 stdnext = arg_gbl.std;
5627 lineno = STD_LINENO(stdnext);
5628 if (1 || !dest) {
5629 int sptr, dtnew, eldtype;
5630 ADSC *ad;
5631 eldtype = DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ast));
5632 if (SHD_NDIM(shape1) == 1) {
5633 dtnew = get_array_dtype(1, eldtype);
5634 ad = AD_DPTR(dtnew);
5635 AD_LWBD(ad, 0) = AD_LWAST(ad, 0) = mk_cval(1, DT_INT);
5636 AD_UPBD(ad, 0) = AD_UPAST(ad, 0) = mk_cval(jextent, DT_INT);
5637 AD_EXTNTAST(ad, 0) = AD_UPBD(ad, 0);
5638 } else if (SHD_NDIM(shape2) == 1) {
5639 dtnew = get_array_dtype(1, eldtype);
5640 ad = AD_DPTR(dtnew);
5641 AD_LWBD(ad, 0) = AD_LWAST(ad, 0) = mk_cval(1, DT_INT);
5642 AD_UPBD(ad, 0) = AD_UPAST(ad, 0) = mk_cval(iextent, DT_INT);
5643 AD_EXTNTAST(ad, 0) = AD_UPBD(ad, 0);
5644 } else {
5645 dtnew = get_array_dtype(2, eldtype);
5646 ad = AD_DPTR(dtnew);
5647 AD_LWBD(ad, 0) = AD_LWAST(ad, 0) = mk_cval(1, DT_INT);
5648 AD_UPBD(ad, 0) = AD_UPAST(ad, 0) = mk_cval(iextent, DT_INT);
5649 AD_EXTNTAST(ad, 0) = AD_UPBD(ad, 0);
5650 AD_LWBD(ad, 1) = AD_LWAST(ad, 1) = mk_cval(1, DT_INT);
5651 AD_UPBD(ad, 1) = AD_UPAST(ad, 1) = mk_cval(jextent, DT_INT);
5652 AD_EXTNTAST(ad, 1) = AD_UPBD(ad, 1);
5653 }
5654 sptr = get_arr_temp(dtnew, TRUE, FALSE, FALSE);
5655 trans_mkdescr(sptr);
5656 dest = mk_id(sptr);
5657 }
5658 arraydest = convert_subscript_in_expr(dest);
5659 mulop = OP_MUL;
5660 addop = OP_ADD;
5661 if (TY_ISLOG(DTYG(A_DTYPEG(ast)))) {
5662 mulop = OP_LAND;
5663 addop = OP_LOR;
5664 } else if (!TY_ISNUMERIC(DTYG(A_DTYPEG(ast)))) {
5665 return ast;
5666 }
5667 /* build assignment statements */
5668 for (j = 0; j < jextent; ++j) {
5669 for (i = 0; i < iextent; ++i) {
5670 int lhs, rhs, std;
5671 if (SHD_NDIM(shape1) == 1) {
5672 lhs = build_array_ref(arraydest, 0, j, 1, i);
5673 } else {
5674 lhs = build_array_ref(arraydest, 0, i, 1, j);
5675 }
5676 if (lhs == 0)
5677 return ast;
5678 rhs = 0;
5679 for (k = 0; k < kextent; ++k) {
5680 int opnd1, opnd2;
5681 opnd1 = build_array_ref(array1, ii, i, kk, k);
5682 if (opnd1 == 0)
5683 return ast;
5684 opnd2 = build_array_ref(array2, 0, k, 1, j);
5685 if (opnd2 == 0)
5686 return ast;
5687 opnd1 = mk_binop(mulop, opnd1, opnd2, A_DTYPEG(opnd1));
5688 if (!rhs) {
5689 rhs = opnd1;
5690 } else {
5691 rhs = mk_binop(addop, rhs, opnd1, A_DTYPEG(opnd1));
5692 }
5693 }
5694 lhs = mk_assn_stmt(lhs, rhs, A_DTYPEG(rhs));
5695 std = add_stmt_before(lhs, stdnext);
5696 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
5697 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
5698 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
5699 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
5700 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
5701 }
5702 }
5703 /* return the destination array */
5704 return arraydest;
5705} /* inline_small_matmul */
5706
5707static int
5708inline_reduction_f90(int ast, int dest, int lc, LOGICAL *doremove)
5709{
5710 int astdim, dim, mask, astmask;
5711 int args;
5712 int src1, src2, std;
5713 int dtype, dtypetmp, dtyperes, dtsclr, eldtype;
5714 int dtypetmpval, sptrtmpval, asttmpval, dtypeval, astsubscrtmpval;
5715 int dealloc_tmpval = FALSE;
5716 int srcarray;
5717 int home, homeforall;
5718 int lb, ub, st;
5719 int forall;
5720 int asn;
5721 int lineno;
5722 int stdnext;
5723 int newast;
5724 int ast2;
5725 int allocobj;
5726 int sptrtmp, asttmp, astsubscrtmp;
5727 int tmpndim;
5728 int i, j, n;
5729 int triplet_list, index_var;
5730 int triplet;
5731 int shape;
5732 int dest_shape;
5733 int sptr;
5734 int ndim, asd;
5735 int list;
5736 int endif_ast, ifastnew;
5737 char sReduc[128];
5738 int ReducType;
5739 int astInit;
5740 int operator, operand;
5741 int ifast, endif;
5742 int dovar;
5743 int subs[MAXSUBS];
5744 int loopidx[MAXSUBS];
5745 int DOs[MAXSUBS];
5746 int curloop;
5747 int tmpidx[MAXSUBS];
5748 int nbrloops;
5749 int destndim;
5750 int destsub;
5751 int destsptr;
5752 int destref;
5753 ADSC *ad;
5754 int dealloc_dest = FALSE;
5755
5756 if (XBIT(47, 0x80))
5757 return ast;
5758 if (A_TYPEG(ast) != A_INTR)
5759 return ast;
5760
5761 /* if not reduction, return */
5762 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
5763 case I_ALL:
5764 case I_ANY:
5765 case I_COUNT:
5766 case I_DOT_PRODUCT:
5767 case I_MAXVAL:
5768 case I_MINVAL:
5769 case I_PRODUCT:
5770 case I_SUM:
5771 if (doremove)
5772 *doremove = TRUE;
5773 break;
5774 case I_MAXLOC:
5775 case I_MINLOC:
5776 return ast;
5777 /* simple cases only */
5778 if (dest) {
5779 if (A_TYPEG(dest) == A_SUBSCR) {
5780 shape = A_SHAPEG(dest);
5781 if (SHD_NDIM(shape) != 1 || SHD_LWB(shape, 0) != SHD_UPB(shape, 0))
5782 return ast;
5783 } else if (A_TYPEG(dest) != A_ID)
5784 return ast;
5785 }
5786 if (doremove)
5787 *doremove = TRUE;
5788 break;
5789 case I_MATMUL:
5790 case I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE:
5791 if (doremove)
5792 *doremove = FALSE;
5793 return inline_small_matmul(ast, dest);
5794 default:
5795 return ast;
5796 }
5797
5798 /* collect args */
5799 mask = 0;
5800 strcpy(sReduc, SYMNAME(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast))));
5801 dtype = A_DTYPEG(ast);
5802 dtyperes = DDTG(dtype);
5803 args = A_ARGSG(ast);
5804 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
5805 case I_SUM:
5806 case I_PRODUCT:
5807 astdim = ARGT_ARG(args, 1);
5808 mask = ARGT_ARG(args, 2);
5809 srcarray = ARGT_ARG(args, 0);
5810 if (arg_gbl.inforall)
5811 if (contiguous_section_array(srcarray))
5812 return ast;
5813 break;
5814 case I_MAXLOC:
5815 case I_MINLOC:
5816 dtypeval = DDTG(A_DTYPEG(ARGT_ARG(args, 0)));
5817 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
5818 case I_MAXVAL:
5819 case I_MINVAL:
5820 astdim = ARGT_ARG(args, 1);
5821 mask = ARGT_ARG(args, 2);
5822 srcarray = ARGT_ARG(args, 0);
5823 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_CHAR || DTYG(dtype) == TY_NCHAR)
5824 return ast;
5825 if (arg_gbl.inforall)
5826 if (contiguous_section_array(srcarray))
5827 return ast;
5828 break;
5829 case I_DOT_PRODUCT:
5830 astdim = 0;
5831 src1 = ARGT_ARG(args, 0);
5832 src2 = ARGT_ARG(args, 1);
5833 if (DT_ISCMPLX(DDTG(dtype)) && (XBIT(70, 0x4000000)
5834 || dtyperes == DT_QCMPLX
5835 ))
5836 return ast;
5837 if (arg_gbl.inforall) {
5838 if (contiguous_section_array(src1) && contiguous_section_array(src2))
5839 return ast;
5840 }
5841 if (DT_ISLOG(DDTG(dtype)))
5842 operator= OP_LAND;
5843 else
5844 operator= OP_MUL;
5845 if (DT_ISCMPLX(DDTG(dtype))) {
5846 int newargt, conjg, nast;
5847 if (dtyperes == DT_CMPLX) {
5848 conjg = I_CONJG;
5849 } else if (dtyperes == DT_CMPLX16) {
5850 conjg = I_DCONJG;
5851 } else {
5852 return ast;
5853 }
5854 newargt = mk_argt(1);
5855 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = src1;
5856 nast = mk_func_node(A_INTR, mk_id(intast_sym[conjg]), 1, newargt);
5857 A_OPTYPEP(nast, conjg);
5858 A_DTYPEP(nast, A_DTYPEG(src1));
5859 src1 = nast;
5860 }
5861 srcarray = mk_binop(operator, src1, src2, dtype);
5862 break;
5863 case I_ALL:
5864 case I_ANY:
5865 case I_COUNT:
5866 astdim = ARGT_ARG(args, 1);
5867 srcarray = ARGT_ARG(args, 0);
5868 if (arg_gbl.inforall)
5869 if (contiguous_section_array(srcarray))
5870 return ast;
5871 break;
5872 }
5873
5874 if (astdim) {
5875 if (A_TYPEG(astdim) != A_CNST) {
5876 return ast;
5877 }
5878 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(astdim));
5879 } else {
5880 dim = 0;
5881 }
5882
5883 if ((A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MAXLOC || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MINLOC) && dim > 1)
5884 return ast;
5885
5886 if (!XBIT(70, 0x1000000) && dim == 1 && arg_gbl.inforall) {
5887 return ast;
5888 }
5889
5890 srcarray = rewrite_scalar_functions(srcarray, arg_gbl.std);
5891 if (contains_any_call(srcarray)) { /* return ast; */
5892 srcarray = rewrite_sub_ast(srcarray, 0);
5893 if (srcarray == -1)
5894 /* source is not something convert_subscript can handle and
5895 * computing it into an allocated temp is probably too
5896 * expensive. Don't inline it; call the subroutine.
5897 */
5898 return ast;
5899 home = search_conform_array(srcarray, TRUE);
5900 if (!home)
5901 /* source is not something convert_subscript can handle and
5902 * computing it into an allocated temp is probably too
5903 * expensive. Don't inline it; call the subroutine.
5904 */
5905 return ast;
5906 if (A_TYPEG(home) != A_ID && A_TYPEG(home) != A_MEM &&
5907 A_TYPEG(home) != A_TRIPLE && A_TYPEG(home) != A_SUBSCR)
5908 /* source is not something convert_subscript can handle and
5909 * computing it into an allocated temp is probably too
5910 * expensive. Don't inline it; call the subroutine.
5911 */
5912 return ast;
5913 /*
5914 fprintf(STDERR,
5915 "%s:%s:%d - inline_reduction_f90 change in behavior\n",
5916 gbl.src_file,
5917 SYMNAME(gbl.currsub), gbl.lineno);
5918 dbg_print_ast(srcarray, 0);
5919 dump_one_ast(srcarray);
5920 */
5921 }
5922 home = search_conform_array(srcarray, TRUE);
5923 if (!home)
5924 return ast;
5925 if (mask) {
5926 mask = rewrite_scalar_functions(mask, arg_gbl.std);
5927 if (contains_any_call(mask)) { /* return ast; */
5928 mask = rewrite_sub_ast(mask, 0);
5929 if (mask == -1) {
5930 /* source is not something convert_subscript can handle and
5931 * computing it into an allocated temp is probably too
5932 * expensive. Don't inline it; call the subroutine.
5933 */
5934 return ast;
5935 }
5936 }
5937 }
5938 ast2 = convert_subscript_in_expr(srcarray);
5939 home = convert_subscript(home);
5940 if (mask) {
5941 astmask = convert_subscript_in_expr(mask);
5942 } else {
5943 astmask = 0;
5944 }
5945
5946 sptr = sptr_of_subscript(home);
5947
5948 shape = A_SHAPEG(home);
5949 forall = make_forall(shape, home, astmask,
5950 lc + SHD_NDIM(shape)); /*TODO: need correct triple */
5951 homeforall = normalize_forall(forall, home, 0);
5952 ast2 = normalize_forall(forall, ast2, 0);
5953 if (mask) {
5954 astmask = normalize_forall(forall, astmask, 0);
5955 }
5956 list = A_LISTG(forall);
5957 asd = A_ASDG(homeforall);
5958 ndim = ASD_NDIM(asd); /* MORE ndim and nbrloops are NOT the same!!! */
5959 nbrloops = SHD_NDIM(shape);
5960
5961 stdnext = arg_gbl.std;
5962 lineno = STD_LINENO(stdnext);
5963
5964 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MAXLOC || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MINLOC) {
5965 /* build temp */
5966 sptrtmp = sym_get_scalar(SYMNAME(sptr), "r", dtyperes);
5967 dtypetmp = DTYPEG(sptrtmp);
5968 asttmp = mk_id(sptrtmp);
5969 dtypetmp = DTYPEG(sptrtmp);
5970 asttmp = mk_id(sptrtmp);
5971
5972 /* build temp to hold values for I_MAXLOC, I_MINLOC */
5973 if (dim <= 1 || nbrloops == 1) {
5974 sptrtmpval = sym_get_scalar(SYMNAME(sptr), "vr", dtypeval);
5975 dtypetmpval = DTYPEG(sptrtmpval);
5976 asttmpval = mk_id(sptrtmpval);
5977 } else {
5978 reset_init_idx();
5979 dest_shape = A_SHAPEG(ast);
5980 sptrtmpval = sym_get_array(SYMNAME(sptr), "vr", dtypeval, dim - 1);
5981 dtypetmpval = DTYPEG(sptrtmpval);
5982 for (i = 0; i < dim - 1; ++i) {
5983 ADD_LWBD(dtypetmpval, i) = ADD_LWAST(dtypetmpval, i) =
5984 SHD_LWB(dest_shape, i);
5985 ADD_UPBD(dtypetmpval, i) = ADD_UPAST(dtypetmpval, i) =
5986 SHD_UPB(dest_shape, i);
5987 ADD_EXTNTAST(dtypetmpval, i) =
5988 mk_extent(ADD_LWAST(dtypetmpval, i), ADD_UPAST(dtypetmpval, i), i);
5989 subs[i] = mk_triple(SHD_LWB(dest_shape, i), SHD_UPB(dest_shape, i),
5990 astb.bnd.one);
5991 }
5992 dtypetmpval = DTYPEG(sptrtmpval);
5993 NODESCP(sptrtmpval, 1);
5994 check_small_allocatable(sptrtmpval);
5995 asttmpval = mk_id(sptrtmpval);
5996
5997 if (ALLOCG(sptrtmpval)) {
5998 allocobj = mk_subscr(asttmpval, subs, dim - 1, DDTG(dtypetmpval));
5999 newast = mk_stmt(A_ALLOC, 0);
6000 A_TKNP(newast, TK_ALLOCATE);
6001 A_LOPP(newast, 0);
6002 A_SRCP(newast, allocobj);
6003 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
6004 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6005 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6006 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6007 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6008 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6009 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6010 if (STD_ACCEL(std))
6011 STD_RESCOPE(std) = 1;
6012 dealloc_tmpval = TRUE;
6013 }
6014 }
6015 } else {
6016 /* build temp */
6017 if (dim <= 1 || nbrloops == 1) {
6018 sptrtmp = sym_get_scalar(SYMNAME(sptr), "r", dtyperes);
6019 dtypetmp = DTYPEG(sptrtmp);
6020 asttmp = mk_id(sptrtmp);
6021 } else {
6022 reset_init_idx();
6023 dest_shape = A_SHAPEG(ast);
6024 sptrtmp = sym_get_array(SYMNAME(sptr), "r", dtyperes, dim - 1);
6025 dtypetmp = DTYPEG(sptrtmp);
6026 ad = AD_DPTR(dtype);
6027 for (i = 0; i < dim - 1; ++i) {
6028 if (SHD_STRIDE(dest_shape, i) == astb.i1 ||
6029 SHD_STRIDE(dest_shape, i) == astb.bnd.one) {
6030 ADD_LWBD(dtypetmp, i) = ADD_LWAST(dtypetmp, i) =
6031 SHD_LWB(dest_shape, i);
6032 ADD_UPBD(dtypetmp, i) = ADD_UPAST(dtypetmp, i) =
6033 SHD_UPB(dest_shape, i);
6034 ADD_EXTNTAST(dtypetmp, i) =
6035 mk_extent(ADD_LWAST(dtypetmp, i), ADD_UPAST(dtypetmp, i), i);
6036 subs[i] = mk_triple(SHD_LWB(dest_shape, i), SHD_UPB(dest_shape, i),
6037 astb.bnd.one);
6038 } else {
6039 ADD_LWBD(dtypetmp, i) = ADD_LWAST(dtypetmp, i) =
6040 SHD_LWB(dest_shape, i);
6041 ADD_UPBD(dtypetmp, i) = ADD_UPAST(dtypetmp, i) = mk_binop(
6042 OP_DIV,
6043 mk_binop(OP_ADD,
6044 mk_binop(OP_SUB, SHD_UPB(dest_shape, i),
6045 SHD_LWB(dest_shape, i), astb.bnd.dtype),
6046 SHD_STRIDE(dest_shape, i), astb.bnd.dtype),
6047 SHD_STRIDE(dest_shape, i), astb.bnd.dtype);
6048
6049 ADD_EXTNTAST(dtypetmp, i) =
6050 mk_extent(ADD_LWAST(dtypetmp, i), ADD_UPAST(dtypetmp, i), i);
6051 subs[i] = mk_triple(ADD_LWAST(dtypetmp, i), ADD_UPAST(dtypetmp, i),
6052 astb.bnd.one);
6053 }
6054 }
6055 dtypetmp = DTYPEG(sptrtmp);
6056 NODESCP(sptrtmp, 1);
6057 check_small_allocatable(sptrtmp);
6058 asttmp = mk_id(sptrtmp);
6059
6060 if (ALLOCG(sptrtmp)) {
6061 allocobj = mk_subscr(asttmp, subs, dim - 1, DDTG(dtypetmp));
6062 newast = mk_stmt(A_ALLOC, 0);
6063 A_TKNP(newast, TK_ALLOCATE);
6064 A_LOPP(newast, 0);
6065 A_SRCP(newast, allocobj);
6066 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
6067 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6068 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6069 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6070 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6071 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6072 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6073 if (STD_ACCEL(std))
6074 STD_RESCOPE(std) = 1;
6075 }
6076 }
6077 }
6078
6079 /* if necessary, build destination */
6080 if (!dest) {
6081 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
6082 if (DTY(dtypetmp) == TY_ARRAY && ADD_NUMDIM(dtypetmp) == ndim - 1) {
6083 /* use temp from above as dest */
6084 destsptr = sptrtmp;
6085 dest = asttmp;
6086 NODESCP(sptrtmp, 0);
6087 trans_mkdescr(destsptr); /* MORE is this needed??? */
6088 } else {
6089 ADSC *addest;
6090 reset_init_idx();
6091 destsptr = sym_get_array(SYMNAME(sptr), "tr", dtyperes, nbrloops - 1);
6092 addest = AD_DPTR(DTYPEG(destsptr));
6093 AD_NUMDIM(addest) = nbrloops - 1;
6094 j = 0;
6095 shape = A_SHAPEG(home);
6096 for (i = 0; i < nbrloops; ++i) {
6097 if (i != dim - 1) {
6098 AD_LWAST(addest, j) = AD_LWBD(addest, j) = SHD_LWB(shape, i);
6099 AD_UPAST(addest, j) = AD_UPBD(addest, j) = SHD_UPB(shape, i);
6100 AD_EXTNTAST(addest, j) =
6101 mk_extent(AD_LWAST(addest, j), AD_UPAST(addest, j), j);
6102 subs[j] = mk_triple(AD_LWBD(addest, j), AD_UPBD(addest, j),
6103 SHD_STRIDE(shape, i));
6104 j++;
6105 }
6106 }
6107 dest = mk_id(destsptr);
6108 A_SHAPEP(dest, reduc_shape(shape, astdim, STD_PREV(stdnext)));
6109
6110 trans_mkdescr(destsptr); /* MORE is this needed??? */
6111 check_small_allocatable(destsptr);
6112
6113 if (ALLOCG(destsptr)) {
6114 allocobj = mk_subscr(dest, subs, nbrloops - 1, dtyperes);
6115 newast = mk_stmt(A_ALLOC, 0);
6116 A_TKNP(newast, TK_ALLOCATE);
6117 A_LOPP(newast, 0);
6118 A_SRCP(newast, allocobj);
6119 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
6120 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6121 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6122 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6123 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6124 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6125 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6126 if (STD_ACCEL(std))
6127 STD_RESCOPE(std) = 1;
6128 dealloc_dest = TRUE;
6129 }
6130 }
6131 } else {
6132 dest = asttmp;
6133 }
6134 }
6135
6136 /* select reduction type */
6137
6138 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
6139 case I_SUM:
6140 case I_COUNT:
6141 ReducType = I_REDUCE_SUM;
6142 astInit = mk_convert(astb.i0, DDTG(dtypetmp));
6143 break;
6144 case I_DOT_PRODUCT:
6145 ReducType = I_REDUCE_SUM;
6146 if (DT_ISLOG(DDTG(dtypetmp)))
6147 astInit = mk_cval(SCFTN_FALSE, DT_LOG);
6148 else
6149 astInit = mk_convert(astb.i0, DDTG(dtypetmp));
6150 break;
6151 case I_PRODUCT:
6152 ReducType = I_REDUCE_PRODUCT;
6153 astInit = mk_convert(astb.i1, DDTG(dtypetmp));
6154 break;
6155 case I_MAXVAL:
6156 ReducType = I_REDUCE_MAXVAL;
6157 astInit = mk_smallest_val(DDTG(dtypetmp));
6158 break;
6159 case I_MAXLOC:
6160 ReducType = I_REDUCE_MAXVAL;
6161 astInit = mk_smallest_val(DDTG(dtypetmpval));
6162 break;
6163 case I_MINVAL:
6164 ReducType = I_REDUCE_MINVAL;
6165 astInit = mk_largest_val(DDTG(dtypetmp));
6166 break;
6167 case I_MINLOC:
6168 ReducType = I_REDUCE_MINVAL;
6169 astInit = mk_largest_val(DDTG(dtypetmpval));
6170 break;
6171 case I_ALL:
6172 ReducType = I_REDUCE_ALL;
6173 astInit = mk_cval(SCFTN_TRUE, DDTG(dtypetmp));
6174 break;
6175 case I_ANY:
6176 ReducType = I_REDUCE_ANY;
6177 astInit = mk_cval(SCFTN_FALSE, DDTG(dtypetmp));
6178 break;
6179 default:
6180 assert(0, "inline_reduction_f90: unknown type", ast, 4);
6181 }
6182
6183 if (dim == 0) {
6184 /* initialize temp */
6185 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MAXLOC || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MINLOC)
6186 asn = mk_assn_stmt(asttmpval, astInit, dtypetmpval);
6187 else
6188 asn = mk_assn_stmt(asttmp, astInit, dtypetmp);
6189 std = add_stmt_before(asn, stdnext);
6190 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6191 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6192 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6193 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6194 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6195 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6196 }
6197
6198 n = nbrloops;
6199 j = nbrloops - 1;
6200 triplet_list = A_LISTG(forall);
6201 for (; triplet_list; triplet_list = ASTLI_NEXT(triplet_list)) {
6202 index_var = ASTLI_SPTR(triplet_list);
6203 /* find the matching home dimension */
6204 for (i = 0; i < ndim; i++)
6205 if (is_name_in_expr(ASD_SUBS(asd, i), index_var))
6206 break;
6207 triplet = ASTLI_TRIPLE(triplet_list);
6208 st = A_STRIDEG(triplet);
6209 if (!st)
6210 st = astb.i1;
6211
6212 newast = mk_stmt(A_DO, 0);
6213 lb = A_LBDG(triplet);
6214 ub = A_UPBDG(triplet);
6215
6216 dovar = mk_id(index_var);
6217 loopidx[j] = dovar;
6218 A_DOVARP(newast, dovar);
6219 A_M1P(newast, lb);
6220 A_M2P(newast, ub);
6221 A_M3P(newast, st);
6222 A_M4P(newast, 0);
6223 DOs[j] = newast;
6224
6225 if (n-- == dim) {
6226 /* initialize temp */
6227 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MAXLOC || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MINLOC)
6228 asn = mk_assn_stmt(asttmpval, astInit, dtypetmpval);
6229 else
6230 asn = mk_assn_stmt(asttmp, astInit, dtypetmp);
6231 std = add_stmt_before(asn, stdnext);
6232 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6233 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6234 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6235 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6236 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6237 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6238 } else {
6239 tmpidx[j] = dovar;
6240 }
6241
6242 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
6243 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6244 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6245 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6246 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6247 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6248 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6249 i++;
6250 j--;
6251 }
6252
6253 if (mask) {
6254 ifastnew = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
6255 A_IFEXPRP(ifastnew, astmask);
6256 std = add_stmt_before(ifastnew, stdnext);
6257 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6258 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6259 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6260 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6261 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6262 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6263 }
6264
6265 /* select reduction stmt */
6266 if (dim > 1 && nbrloops != 1) {
6267 ad = AD_DPTR(DTYPEG(sptrtmp));
6268 tmpndim = AD_NUMDIM(ad);
6269 for (j = 0; j < tmpndim; i++, j++) {
6270 if (SHD_STRIDE(dest_shape, j) == astb.i1 ||
6271 SHD_STRIDE(dest_shape, j) == astb.bnd.one) {
6272 subs[j] = loopidx[j];
6273 } else
6274 subs[j] = mk_binop(OP_ADD,
6275 mk_binop(OP_DIV, loopidx[j],
6276 SHD_STRIDE(dest_shape, j), astb.bnd.dtype),
6277 SHD_LWB(dest_shape, j), astb.bnd.dtype);
6278 }
6279 astsubscrtmp = mk_subscr(asttmp, subs, tmpndim, DDTG(dtypetmp));
6280 A_SHAPEP(astsubscrtmp, 0);
6281 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MAXLOC || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MINLOC) {
6282 astsubscrtmpval = mk_subscr(asttmpval, subs, tmpndim, DDTG(dtypetmpval));
6283 A_SHAPEP(astsubscrtmpval, 0);
6284 }
6285 } else {
6286 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MAXLOC || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MINLOC) {
6287 astsubscrtmpval = asttmpval;
6288 astsubscrtmp = dest;
6289 } else
6290 astsubscrtmp = asttmp;
6291 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MAXLOC || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MINLOC ||
6292 A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MAXVAL || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MINVAL) {
6293 /* if the expression being reduced is nontrivial, assign to a temp */
6294 if (A_TYPEG(ast2) == A_SUBSCR || A_TYPEG(ast2) == A_ID) {
6295 } else {
6296 /* create a temporary scalar */
6297 int temprhs = sym_get_scalar(SYMNAME(sptr), "l", dtyperes);
6298 /* assign the RHS to temprhs */
6299 int std = mk_assn_stmt(mk_id(temprhs), ast2, dtyperes);
6300 add_stmt_before(std, stdnext);
6301 ast2 = mk_id(temprhs);
6302 }
6303 }
6304 }
6305 dtsclr = DDTG(dtypetmp);
6306 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
6307 case I_SUM:
6308 case I_DOT_PRODUCT:
6309 if (DT_ISLOG(dtsclr))
6310 operator= OP_LOR;
6311 else
6312 operator= OP_ADD;
6313 newast = mk_binop(operator, astsubscrtmp, ast2, dtsclr);
6314 asn = mk_assn_stmt(astsubscrtmp, newast, dtsclr);
6315
6316 std = add_stmt_before(asn, stdnext);
6317 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6318 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6319 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6320 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6321 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6322 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6323 break;
6324 case I_COUNT:
6325 newast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, astsubscrtmp, astb.i1, dtsclr);
6326 asn = mk_assn_stmt(astsubscrtmp, newast, dtsclr);
6327
6328 ifast = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
6329 A_IFEXPRP(ifast, ast2);
6330 std = add_stmt_before(ifast, stdnext);
6331 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6332 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6333 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6334 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6335 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6336 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6337
6338 std = add_stmt_before(asn, stdnext);
6339 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6340 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6341 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6342 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6343 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6344 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6345
6346 endif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
6347 std = add_stmt_before(endif, stdnext);
6348 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6349 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6350 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6351 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6352 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6353 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6354 break;
6355 case I_PRODUCT:
6356 newast = mk_binop(OP_MUL, astsubscrtmp, ast2, dtsclr);
6357 asn = mk_assn_stmt(astsubscrtmp, newast, dtsclr);
6358 std = add_stmt_before(asn, stdnext);
6359 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6360 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6361 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6362 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6363 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6364 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6365 break;
6366 case I_MAXVAL:
6367 newast = mk_binop(OP_GT, ast2, astsubscrtmp, DT_LOG);
6368 asn = mk_assn_stmt(astsubscrtmp, ast2, dtsclr);
6369 goto max_min_common;
6370 case I_MINVAL:
6371 newast = mk_binop(OP_LT, ast2, astsubscrtmp, DT_LOG);
6372 asn = mk_assn_stmt(astsubscrtmp, ast2, dtsclr);
6373 goto max_min_common;
6374 case I_MAXLOC:
6375 newast = mk_binop(OP_GT, ast2, astsubscrtmpval, DT_LOG);
6376 asn = mk_assn_stmt(astsubscrtmpval, ast2, DDTG(dtypetmpval));
6377 goto max_min_common;
6378 case I_MINLOC:
6379 newast = mk_binop(OP_LT, ast2, astsubscrtmpval, DT_LOG);
6380 asn = mk_assn_stmt(astsubscrtmpval, ast2, DDTG(dtypetmpval));
6381
6382 max_min_common:
6383 ifast = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
6384 A_IFEXPRP(ifast, newast);
6385 std = add_stmt_before(ifast, stdnext);
6386 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6387 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6388 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6389 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6390 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6391 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6392
6393 std = add_stmt_before(asn, stdnext);
6394 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6395 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6396 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6397 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6398 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6399 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6400
6401 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MAXLOC || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_MINLOC) {
6402 if (nbrloops > 1) {
6403 for (j = 0; j < nbrloops; j++) {
6404 int subscr;
6405
6406 subscr = mk_cval(j + 1, astb.bnd.dtype);
6407 ast2 = mk_subscr(astsubscrtmp, &subscr, 1, dtyperes);
6408 asn = mk_assn_stmt(ast2, A_DOVARG(DOs[j]), dtyperes);
6409 std = add_stmt_before(asn, stdnext);
6410 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6411 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6412 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6413 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6414 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6415 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6416 }
6417 } else {
6418 asn = mk_assn_stmt(astsubscrtmp, A_DOVARG(DOs[0]), dtyperes);
6419 std = add_stmt_before(asn, stdnext);
6420 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6421 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6422 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6423 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6424 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6425 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6426 }
6427 }
6428
6429 endif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
6430 std = add_stmt_before(endif, stdnext);
6431 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6432 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6433 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6434 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6435 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6436 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6437 break;
6438 case I_ALL:
6439 case I_ANY:
6440 if (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == I_ALL) {
6441 newast = mk_unop(OP_LNOT, ast2, DT_LOG);
6442 operand = mk_cval(SCFTN_FALSE, DT_LOG);
6443 } else {
6444 newast = ast2;
6445 operand = mk_cval(SCFTN_TRUE, DT_LOG);
6446 }
6447 asn = mk_assn_stmt(astsubscrtmp, operand, dtsclr);
6448
6449 ifast = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
6450 A_IFEXPRP(ifast, newast);
6451 std = add_stmt_before(ifast, stdnext);
6452 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6453 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6454 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6455 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6456 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6457 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6458
6459 std = add_stmt_before(asn, stdnext);
6460 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6461 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6462 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6463 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6464 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6465 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6466
6467 endif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
6468 std = add_stmt_before(endif, stdnext);
6469 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6470 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6471 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6472 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6473 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6474 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6475 break;
6476 default:
6477 assert(0, "inline_reduction_f90: unknown type", ast, 4);
6478 }
6479
6480 if (mask) {
6481 endif_ast = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
6482 std = add_stmt_before(endif_ast, stdnext);
6483 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6484 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6485 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6486 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6487 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6488 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6489 }
6490
6491 destref = dest;
6492 eldtype = dtypetmp; /* assume subscripted object is the immediate lhs */
6493 destsptr = memsym_of_ast(dest);
6494 ast2 = search_conform_array(dest, TRUE);
6495 if (ast2) {
6496 /* array-valued result. The result could be something like
6497 * dt(:)%mem, du%amem(:), arr(:)
6498 * Need to locate the array in the lhs which needs to be subscripted.
6499 */
6500 int ss;
6501 if (A_TYPEG(ast2) == A_SUBSCR)
6502 ss = sptr_of_subscript(ast2);
6503 else
6504 ss = memsym_of_ast(ast2);
6505 if (ss != destsptr) {
6506 /* subscripted object is some aggregate */
6507 destsptr = ss;
6508 eldtype = DTY(DTYPEG(destsptr) + 1);
6509 destref = ast2;
6510 }
6511 }
6512 ast2 = mk_id(destsptr);
6513 ast2 = check_member(ast_is_sym(dest) &&
6514 (sym_of_ast(dest) != pass_sym_of_ast(dest))
6515 ? A_PARENTG(dest)
6516 : dest,
6517 ast2);
6518 ad = AD_DPTR(DTYPEG(destsptr));
6519 destndim = AD_NUMDIM(ad);
6520 for (i = 1; i <= nbrloops; i++) {
6521 newast = mk_stmt(A_ENDDO, 0);
6522 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
6523 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6524 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6525 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6526 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6527 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6528 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6529 if (i == dim && destref != asttmp) {
6530 if (nbrloops > 1) {
6531 if (A_TYPEG(destref) == A_SUBSCR) {
6532 asd = A_ASDG(destref);
6533 curloop = 0;
6534 for (j = 0; j < destndim; j++) {
6535 destsub = ASD_SUBS(asd, j);
6536 if (A_TYPEG(destsub) != A_TRIPLE) {
6537 subs[j] = destsub;
6538 } else if (curloop < dim - 1) {
6539 subs[j] = destsub;
6540 curloop++;
6541 } else {
6542 /*
6543 * for DO i$a = m1, m2, m3
6544 * the subscripting of
6545 * dest(lb:ub:st)
6546 *
6547 * ( (i$a - m1)/m3 ) * st + lb
6548 *
6549 */
6550 int o;
6551 int mdo;
6552 subs[j] = loopidx[++curloop];
6553 mdo = DOs[curloop];
6554 o = mk_binop(OP_SUB, subs[j], A_M1G(mdo), astb.bnd.dtype);
6555 if ((A_M3G(mdo) != astb.i1) && (A_M3G(mdo) != astb.k1))
6556 o = mk_binop(OP_DIV, o, A_M3G(mdo), astb.bnd.dtype);
6557 if (A_STRIDEG(destsub))
6558 o = mk_binop(OP_MUL, o, A_STRIDEG(destsub), astb.bnd.dtype);
6559 o = mk_binop(OP_ADD, o, A_LBDG(destsub), astb.bnd.dtype);
6560 subs[j] = o;
6561 }
6562 }
6563 } else {
6564 for (j = 0; j < destndim; j++) {
6565 if (j < dim - 1) {
6566 int lb, ub;
6567 lb = check_member(destref, AD_LWBD(ad, j));
6568 ub = check_member(destref, AD_UPBD(ad, j));
6569 subs[j] = mk_triple(lb, ub, astb.bnd.one);
6570 } else {
6571 subs[j] = loopidx[j + 1];
6572 }
6573 }
6574 }
6575 ast2 = subscript_lhs(ast2, subs, destndim, eldtype, dest, destref);
6576 ast2 = convert_subscript_in_expr(ast2);
6577 ast2 = mk_assn_stmt(ast2, asttmp, dtypetmp);
6578 std = add_stmt_before(ast2, stdnext);
6579 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6580 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6581 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6582 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6583 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6584 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6585 }
6586 }
6587 }
6588
6589 if (ALLOCG(sptrtmp)) {
6590 newast = mk_stmt(A_ALLOC, 0);
6591 A_TKNP(newast, TK_DEALLOCATE);
6592 A_LOPP(newast, 0);
6593 A_SRCP(newast, asttmp);
6594 if (dest != asttmp)
6595 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
6596 else
6597 std = add_stmt_before(newast, STD_NEXT(stdnext));
6598 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6599 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6600 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6601 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6602 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6603 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6604 if (STD_ACCEL(std))
6605 STD_RESCOPE(std) = 1;
6606 }
6607
6608 if (dealloc_tmpval) {
6609 newast = mk_stmt(A_ALLOC, 0);
6610 A_TKNP(newast, TK_DEALLOCATE);
6611 A_LOPP(newast, 0);
6612 A_SRCP(newast, asttmpval);
6613 std = add_stmt_before(newast, stdnext);
6614 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6615 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6616 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6617 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6618 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6619 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6620 if (STD_ACCEL(std))
6621 STD_RESCOPE(std) = 1;
6622 }
6623
6624 if (dealloc_dest) {
6625 newast = mk_stmt(A_ALLOC, 0);
6626 A_TKNP(newast, TK_DEALLOCATE);
6627 A_LOPP(newast, 0);
6628 A_SRCP(newast, dest);
6629 std = add_stmt_before(newast, STD_NEXT(stdnext));
6630 STD_LINENO(std) = lineno;
6631 STD_LOCAL(std) = 1;
6632 STD_PAR(std) = STD_PAR(stdnext);
6633 STD_TASK(std) = STD_TASK(stdnext);
6634 STD_ACCEL(std) = STD_ACCEL(stdnext);
6635 STD_KERNEL(std) = STD_KERNEL(stdnext);
6636 if (STD_ACCEL(std))
6637 STD_RESCOPE(std) = 1;
6638 }
6639
6640 ccff_info(MSGOPT, "OPT022", 1, STD_LINENO(arg_gbl.std),
6641 "%reduction reduction inlined", "reduction=%s", sReduc, NULL);
6642
6643 return dest;
6644}
6645
6646static int
6647subscript_lhs(int arr, int *subs, int dim, DTYPE dtype, int origlhs,
6648 int destref)
6649{
6650 /*
6651 * need to subscript an array in the lhs. The origlhs could be something
6652 * like dt(:)%mem, du%amem(:), arr(:).
6653 * If the array is an aggregate, then need to just replace the array
6654 * in the origlhs with the subscripted form of the array and then apply
6655 * the remaining portion of the lhs; e.g.,
6656 * arr%m1%m2%...mem becomes arr(i$a)%m1%m2%...mem
6657 */
6658 int ast = mk_subscr(arr, subs, dim, dtype);
6659 if (origlhs == destref)
6660 return ast;
6661 ast = replace_ast_subtree(origlhs, destref, ast);
6662 return ast;
6663}
6664
6665/*
6666 * func_ast: A_FUNC or A_INTR
6667 * func_args: rewritten args
6668 * lhs: ast for lhs (temp) if non-zero
6669 */
6670static int
6671matmul(int func_ast, int func_args, int lhs)
6672{
6673 /* func_ast is a function or intrinsic call. If it is a transformational
6674 * intrinsic, create an appropriate temp, rewrite, and return a load
6675 * of that temp.
6676 * For now, don't do anything with user-defined functions.
6677 */
6678 int shape;
6679 DTYPE dtype;
6680 int newsym;
6681 int temp_arr;
6682 int newargt;
6683 int srcarray;
6684 int retval;
6685 int ast;
6686 int nargs;
6687 const char *name;
6688 FtnRtlEnum rtlRtn = RTE_no_rtn;
6689 int subscr[MAXSUBS];
6690 int arg1, arg2;
6691 LOGICAL tmp_lhs_array;
6692 LOGICAL matmul_transpose;
6693
6694 retval = mmul(func_ast, func_args, lhs);
6695 if (retval >= 0)
6696 return retval;
6697
6698 tmp_lhs_array = FALSE;
6699 /* it only handles calls */
6700 shape = A_SHAPEG(func_ast);
6701 dtype = A_DTYPEG(func_ast);
6702
6703 matmul_transpose = A_OPTYPEG(func_ast) == I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE ? TRUE : FALSE;
6704
6705 /*
6706 * A_OPTYPEG(func_ast):
6707 * case I_MATMUL: matmul(matrix_a, matrix_b)
6708 * case I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE: matmul(transpose(matrix_a), matrix_b)
6709 */
6710 switch (DTYG(A_DTYPEG(func_ast))) {
6711 case TY_BINT:
6712 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_int1;
6713 break;
6714 case TY_SINT:
6715 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_int2;
6716 break;
6717 case TY_INT:
6718 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_int4;
6719 break;
6720 case TY_INT8:
6721 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_int8;
6722 break;
6723 case TY_REAL:
6724 if (matmul_transpose) {
6725 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_real4mxv_t;
6726 } else {
6727 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_real4;
6728 }
6729 break;
6730 case TY_DBLE:
6731 if (matmul_transpose) {
6732 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_real8mxv_t;
6733 } else {
6734 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_real8;
6735 }
6736 break;
6737#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
6738 case TY_QUAD:
6739 if (matmul_transpose) {
6740 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_real16mxv_t;
6741 } else {
6742 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_real16;
6743 }
6744 break;
6745#endif
6746 case TY_CMPLX:
6747 if (matmul_transpose) {
6748 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_cplx8mxv_t;
6749 } else {
6750 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_cplx8;
6751 }
6752 break;
6753 case TY_DCMPLX:
6754 if (matmul_transpose) {
6755 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_cplx16mxv_t;
6756 } else {
6757 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_cplx16;
6758 }
6759 break;
6760 case TY_BLOG:
6761 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_log1;
6762 break;
6763 case TY_SLOG:
6764 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_log2;
6765 break;
6766 case TY_LOG:
6767 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_log4;
6768 break;
6769 case TY_LOG8:
6770 rtlRtn = RTE_matmul_log8;
6771 break;
6772 default:
6773 error(456, 3, gbl.lineno, CNULL, CNULL);
6774 }
6775
6776 /* MORE if shape is set appropriately, the requirement that lhs is
6777 * contiguous can be dropped
6778 */
6779 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
6780 arg2 = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
6781 check_arg_isalloc(arg1);
6782 check_arg_isalloc(arg2);
6783
6784 if (matmul_transpose) {
6785 nargs = 4;
6786 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
6787 srcarray = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
6788 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = srcarray;
6789 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 2) = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
6790 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 3) = astb.i1; /* place holder in case we recognize
6791 * more than this one case
6792 */
6793 } else {
6794 /* use general purpose F90 matmul */
6795 nargs = 3;
6796 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
6797 srcarray = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
6798 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = srcarray;
6799 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 2) = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
6800 }
6801
6802 name = mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn);
6803
6804 newsym = sym_mkfunc(name, DT_NONE);
6805 /* get the temp and add the necessary statements */
6806 temp_arr =
6807 mk_result_sptr(func_ast, func_args, subscr, DTY(dtype + 1), lhs, &retval);
6808 if (temp_arr != 0) {
6809 /* add temp_arr as argument */
6810 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = retval;
6811 if (ALLOCG(temp_arr)) {
6812 mk_mem_allocate(mk_id(temp_arr), subscr, arg_gbl.std, 0);
6813 mk_mem_deallocate(mk_id(temp_arr), arg_gbl.std);
6814 }
6815 tmp_lhs_array = TRUE;
6816 } else {
6817 /* lhs was distributed properly for this intr */
6818 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = lhs;
6819 retval = 0;
6820 }
6821 /* add call to function */
6822 /* make every call ICALL iff call changes the first argument and
6823 no side effect, this will help optimizer
6824 */
6825 ast = mk_func_node(A_ICALL, mk_id(newsym), nargs, newargt);
6826 A_OPTYPEP(ast, A_OPTYPEG(func_ast));
6827 add_stmt_before(ast, arg_gbl.std);
6828 return retval;
6829}
6830
6831typedef struct { /* info for each fast matmul array/vector argument */
6832 int rank; /* at most 2 */
6833 int ldim; /* "leading dimension" */
6834 int extent[2]; /* number of elements for each dimension */
6835 int addr; /* beginning address of the argument */
6836} MMUL;
6837static LOGICAL mmul_arg(int, int, MMUL *);
6838static LOGICAL mmul_array(int);
6839static int add_byval(int);
6840
6841/*
6842 * func_ast: A_FUNC or A_INTR
6843 * func_args: rewritten args
6844 * lhs: ast for lhs (temp) if non-zero
6845 */
6846static int
6847mmul(int func_ast, int func_args, int lhs)
6848{
6849 /* func_ast is a function or intrinsic call. If it is a transformational
6850 * intrinsic, create an appropriate temp, rewrite, and return a load
6851 * of that temp.
6852 * For now, don't do anything with user-defined functions.
6853 *
6854 * RTE_mmul_real4(ta,tb,m,n,k,alpha,a,lda,b,ldb,beta,c,ldc)
6855 * performs
6856 *
6857 * C = alpha*MATMUL(op(A), op(B)) + beta*C
6858 * where
6859 * op(X) = X
6860 * op(X) = TRANSPOSE(X)
6861 * op(X) = CONJG(X)
6862 *
6863 * V ta : Integer(32 bits)
6864 * 0: no TRANSPOSE nor CONJG
6865 * 1: TRANSPOSE(A)
6866 * 2: CONJG(A)
6867 * V tb : Integer(32 bits)
6868 * 0: no TRANSPOSE nor CONJG
6869 * 1: TRANSPOSE(B)
6870 * 2: CONJG(B)
6871 * V m : Integer
6872 * The number of rows of (transposed) A and C
6873 * V n : Integer
6874 * The number of columns of B and C
6875 * V k : Integer
6876 * The number of columns of (transposed) A and the number of
6877 * rows of B
6878 * R alpha: <matrix element type>
6879 * The scalar alpha.
6880 * R a : <matrix element type>
6881 * Matrix A.
6882 * V lda : Integer
6883 * Leading dimension of (pre-transposed) A
6884 * R b : <matrix element type>
6885 * Matrix B.
6886 * V ldb : Integer
6887 * Leading dimension of B
6888 * R beta : <matrix element type>
6889 * The scalar beta.
6890 * R c : <matrix element type>
6891 * Output Matrix C.
6892 * V ldc : Integer
6893 * Leading dimension of C
6894 *
6895 * V - pass by value; unless specified, value is a 64-bit integer
6896 * for a 64-bit target and 32-bit, otherwise,
6897 * R - pass by reference
6898 *
6899 * Our interface allows for
6900 * VxM - matmul(vectorA, matrixB) -> vectorC
6901 * MxV - matmul(matrixA, vectorB) -> vectorC
6902 *
6903 * For VxM:
6904 * m = 1
6905 * k = length of A & number of rows of B
6906 * n = number of columns of B and the length of C
6907 * lda = 1
6908 * ldb = as before
6909 * ldc = 1
6910 *
6911 * For MxV:
6912 * m = number of rows of A and the length of C
6913 * k = number of columns of A and the length of B
6914 * n = 1
6915 * lda = as before
6916 * ldb = k
6917 * ldc = m
6918 */
6919 int shape, rank;
6920 int dtype, elem_dty;
6921 int newsym;
6922 int temp_arr;
6923 int newargt;
6924 int arrA, arrB;
6925 INT ta, tb; /* transpose flags, actual values */
6926 MMUL mmA, mmB, mmC;
6927 int alpha, beta; /* ST_CONST symtab entries */
6928 INT num[2];
6929 int retval;
6930 int ast;
6931 int nargs;
6932 int subscr[MAXSUBS];
6933 FtnRtlEnum rtlRtn;
6934
6935 retval = -1;
6936 if (XBIT(47, 0x10000000))
6937 return -1;
6938 /*
6939 * A_OPTYPEG(func_ast):
6940 * case I_MATMUL: matmul(matrix_a, matrix_b)
6941 * case I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE: matmul(transpose(matrix_a), matrix_b)
6942 */
6943 dtype = A_DTYPEG(func_ast);
6944 elem_dty = DTY(dtype + 1);
6945 switch (elem_dty) {
6946 case DT_REAL4:
6947 alpha = stb.flt1;
6948 beta = stb.flt0;
6949 rtlRtn = RTE_mmul_real4;
6950 break;
6951 case DT_REAL8:
6952 alpha = stb.dbl1;
6953 beta = stb.dbl0;
6954 rtlRtn = RTE_mmul_real8;
6955 break;
6956#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
6957 case DT_QUAD:
6958 alpha = stb.quad1;
6959 beta = stb.quad0;
6960 rtlRtn = RTE_mmul_real16;
6961 break;
6962#endif
6963 case DT_CMPLX8:
6964 num[0] = CONVAL2G(stb.flt1);
6965 num[1] = CONVAL2G(stb.flt0);
6966 alpha = getcon(num, DT_CMPLX8);
6967 num[0] = CONVAL2G(stb.flt0);
6968 num[1] = CONVAL2G(stb.flt0);
6969 beta = getcon(num, DT_CMPLX8);
6970 rtlRtn = RTE_mmul_cmplx8;
6971 break;
6972 case DT_CMPLX16:
6973 num[0] = stb.dbl1;
6974 num[1] = stb.dbl0;
6975 alpha = getcon(num, DT_CMPLX16);
6976 num[0] = stb.dbl0;
6977 num[1] = stb.dbl0;
6978 beta = getcon(num, DT_CMPLX16);
6979 rtlRtn = RTE_mmul_cmplx16;
6980 break;
6981 default:
6982 return -1;
6983 }
6984 ta = tb = 0;
6985 if (A_OPTYPEG(func_ast) == I_MATMUL_TRANSPOSE) {
6986 /*
6987 * First argument is a transpose of a 2D matrix.
6988 * Second argument is a vector.
6989 */
6990 ta = 1;
6991 }
6992 /* it only handles calls */
6993 shape = A_SHAPEG(func_ast);
6994 rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
6995
6996 /* MORE if shape is set appropriately, the requirement that lhs is
6997 * contiguous can be dropped
6998 */
6999 arrA = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
7000 arrB = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
7001 if (!mmul_arg(arrA, ta, &mmA))
7002 return -1;
7003 if (!mmul_arg(arrB, 0, &mmB))
7004 return -1;
7005 if (matmul_use_lhs(lhs, rank, elem_dty)) {
7006 if (!mmul_arg(lhs, 0, &mmC))
7007 return -1;
7008 /*
7009 * A question here is if the lhs is not suitable as C, should
7010 * we go ahead and create a temp and call the fast matmul at
7011 * expense of 2 sets of copying memory, i.e.,
7012 * tmp = matmu(A, B);
7013 * C = tmp;
7014 * If YES, need to restructure when/how we perform
7015 * temp_arr = mk_result_sptr(func_ast, ... ;
7016 * which is currently done below ...
7017 */
7018 }
7019 if (mmA.rank == 1) {
7020 /* VxM */
7021 mmA.extent[0] = mmA.extent[1]; /* m is 1 */
7022 mmA.extent[1] = mmB.extent[0]; /* k from B */
7023 mmA.ldim = mmA.extent[0]; /* 1 */
7024 } else if (mmB.rank == 1) {
7025 /* MxV */
7026 /* n is 1 */
7027 mmB.extent[0] = mmA.extent[1]; /* k */
7028 }
7029 nargs = 13;
7030 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
7031 newsym = sym_mkfunc_nodesc(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn), DT_NONE);
7032 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = add_byval(mk_cval1(ta, DT_INT4));
7033 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = add_byval(mk_cval1(tb, DT_INT4));
7034 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 2) = add_byval(mmA.extent[0]); /* m */
7035 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 3) = add_byval(mmB.extent[1]); /* n */
7036 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 4) = add_byval(mmA.extent[1]); /* k */
7037 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 5) = mk_cnst(alpha);
7038 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 6) = mmA.addr;
7039 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 7) = add_byval(mmA.ldim);
7040 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 8) = mmB.addr;
7041 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 9) = add_byval(mmB.ldim);
7042 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 10) = mk_cnst(beta);
7043
7044 /* get the temp and add the necessary statements */
7045 temp_arr =
7046 mk_result_sptr(func_ast, func_args, subscr, DTY(dtype + 1), lhs, &retval);
7047 if (temp_arr != 0) {
7048 /* add temp_arr as argument */
7049 (void)mmul_arg(retval, 0, &mmC);
7050 if (ALLOCG(temp_arr)) {
7051 mk_mem_allocate(mk_id(temp_arr), subscr, arg_gbl.std, 0);
7052 mk_mem_deallocate(mk_id(temp_arr), arg_gbl.std);
7053 }
7054 } else {
7055 /* lhs was distributed properly for this intr */
7056 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 11) = lhs;
7057 retval = 0;
7058 }
7059 if (mmA.rank == 1) {
7060 mmC.ldim = mmA.extent[0]; /* 1 */
7061 }
7062 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 11) = mmC.addr;
7063 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 12) = add_byval(mmC.ldim);
7064
7065 /* add call to function */
7066 /* make every call ICALL iff call changes the first argument and
7067 no side effect, this will help optimizer
7068 */
7069 ast = mk_func_node(A_ICALL, mk_id(newsym), nargs, newargt);
7070 A_OPTYPEP(ast, A_OPTYPEG(func_ast));
7071 add_stmt_before(ast, arg_gbl.std);
7072#if DEBUG
7073 ccff_info(MSGOPT, "OPT049", 1, STD_LINENO(arg_gbl.std),
7074 "MATMUL replaced by call to %mmul", "mmul=%s", mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn),
7075 NULL);
7076#endif
7077
7078 return retval;
7079}
7080
7081static LOGICAL
7082mmul_arg(int arr, int transpose, MMUL *mm)
7083{
7084 int sptr;
7085 int shape;
7086 int ldim;
7087 int rank, i;
7088 int lb, ub, stride;
7089 int m;
7090
7091 sptr = find_array(arr, NULL);
7092 if (POINTERG(sptr)
7093#ifdef CONTIGATTRG
7094 && !CONTIGATTRG(sptr)
7095#endif
7096 )
7097 return FALSE;
7098 shape = A_SHAPEG(arr);
7099 if (!shape)
7100 return FALSE;
7101 mm->rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
7102 if (ASSUMSHPG(sptr) && mm->rank != 1
7103#ifdef CONTIGATTRG
7104 && !CONTIGATTRG(sptr)
7105#endif
7106 ) {
7107 /*
7108 * assumed-shaped arrays are guaranteed to be stride 1 in
7109 * just the first dimension.
7110 */
7111 return FALSE;
7112 }
7113 if (A_TYPEG(arr) == A_ID) {
7114 /* whole */
7115 mm->addr = arr;
7116 } else if (A_TYPEG(arr) == A_MEM) {
7117 /* whole -- allowing unsubscripted members is new as of 5/25/2012;
7118 * so to back out, just add 'return FALSE;' here.
7119 */
7120 mm->addr = arr;
7121 } else if (mmul_array(arr)) {
7122 int asd;
7123 int subscr[MAXSUBS];
7124 asd = A_ASDG(arr);
7125 rank = ASD_NDIM(asd);
7126 for (i = 0; i < rank; ++i) {
7127 int ss;
7128 ss = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
7129 if (A_TYPEG(ss) == A_TRIPLE) {
7130 subscr[i] = A_LBDG(ss);
7131 } else {
7132 subscr[i] = ss;
7133 }
7134 }
7135 mm->addr = mk_subscr(A_LOPG(arr), subscr, rank, DDTG(A_DTYPEG(arr)));
7136 } else
7137 return FALSE;
7138
7139 for (i = 0; i < mm->rank; i++) {
7140 lb = SHD_LWB(shape, i);
7141 ub = SHD_UPB(shape, i);
7142 stride = SHD_STRIDE(shape, i);
7143 m = mk_binop(OP_SUB, ub, lb, astb.bnd.dtype);
7144 m = mk_binop(OP_ADD, m, stride, astb.bnd.dtype);
7145 mm->extent[i] = m;
7146 }
7147 /* ldim must be before any tranpose */
7148 if (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_MEMBER) {
7149 return FALSE;
7150 }
7151#ifdef NOEXTENTG
7152 else if (HCCSYMG(sptr) && SCG(sptr) == SC_LOCAL && ALLOCG(sptr) &&
7153 (NOEXTENTG(sptr) || simply_contiguous(arr))) {
7154 /*
7155 * the EXTNTAST temp may not be defined for compiler-created
7156 * allocatable temps assigned the value of the argument.
7157 */
7158 ADSC *tad;
7159 tad = AD_DPTR(DTYPEG(sptr));
7160 ldim = mk_extent_expr(AD_LWBD(tad, 0), AD_UPBD(tad, 0));
7161 }
7162#endif
7163#ifdef CONTIGATTRG
7164 else if (CONTIGATTRG(sptr)) {
7165 ADSC *tad;
7166 tad = AD_DPTR(DTYPEG(sptr));
7167 ldim = mk_extent_expr(AD_LWBD(tad, 0), AD_UPBD(tad, 0));
7168 }
7169#endif
7170 else
7171 return FALSE;
7172 if (transpose) {
7173 /* extents are post-tranposed */
7174 m = mm->extent[0];
7175 mm->extent[0] = mm->extent[1];
7176 mm->extent[1] = m;
7177 }
7178 if (astb.bnd.dtype != DT_INT8) {
7179 ldim = mk_convert(ldim, DT_INT8);
7180 for (i = 0; i < mm->rank; i++) {
7181 mm->extent[i] = mk_convert(mm->extent[i], DT_INT8);
7182 }
7183 }
7184 if (mm->rank == 1)
7185 mm->extent[1] = astb.k1;
7186 mm->ldim = ldim;
7187 return TRUE;
7188}
7189
7190/* Check if each section is contiguous or whole */
7191static LOGICAL
7192mmul_array(int arr_ast)
7193{
7194 int asd, ss;
7195 int ndims, dim;
7196 int ast1;
7197 LOGICAL any;
7198
7199 ast1 = A_TYPEG(arr_ast) == A_MEM ? A_MEMG(arr_ast) : arr_ast;
7200 if (!ast1)
7201 return FALSE;
7202
7203 if (!A_SHAPEG(ast1) || A_TYPEG(ast1) == A_ID)
7204 return TRUE;
7205 asd = A_ASDG(ast1);
7206 ndims = ASD_NDIM(asd);
7207 any = FALSE;
7208 for (dim = ndims - 1; dim >= 0; dim--) {
7209 ss = ASD_SUBS(asd, dim);
7210 if (A_TYPEG(ss) == A_TRIPLE) {
7211 if (!stride1_triple(ss)) {
7212 return FALSE;
7213 }
7214 any = TRUE;
7215 continue;
7216 }
7217 if (DTY(A_DTYPEG(ss)) == TY_ARRAY) {
7218 /*
7219 * No vector indexing ...
7220 */
7221 return FALSE;
7222 }
7223 if (any) {
7224 /*
7225 * The sections must be in consecutive leading dimensions
7226 */
7227 return FALSE;
7228 }
7229 }
7230 return TRUE;
7231}
7232
7233static int
7234add_byval(int arg)
7235{
7236 int ast;
7237 ast = mk_unop(OP_VAL, arg, A_DTYPEG(arg));
7238 return ast;
7239}
7240
7241/* reshape(source, shape, [pad, order]) */
7242static int
7243reshape(int func_ast, int func_args, int lhs)
7244{
7245 int dtype;
7246 int newsym;
7247 int temp_arr;
7248 int newargt;
7249 int srcarray;
7250 int retval;
7251 int ast;
7252 int nargs;
7253 FtnRtlEnum rtlRtn;
7254 int subscr[MAXSUBS];
7255 int ast_from_len;
7256 LOGICAL tmp_lhs_array;
7257
7258 dtype = A_DTYPEG(func_ast);
7259 retval = _reshape(func_args, dtype, lhs);
7260 if (retval > 0) {
7261 return retval;
7262 }
7263 ast_from_len = 0;
7264 tmp_lhs_array = FALSE;
7265 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_CHAR) {
7266 rtlRtn = RTE_reshapeca;
7267 if (DDTG(dtype) == DT_ASSCHAR || DDTG(dtype) == DT_ASSNCHAR ||
7268 DDTG(dtype) == DT_DEFERCHAR || DDTG(dtype) == DT_DEFERNCHAR) {
7269 ast_from_len = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
7270 }
7271 } else
7272 rtlRtn = RTE_reshape;
7273 nargs = 5;
7274 srcarray = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
7275 newargt = mk_argt(nargs);
7276 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = srcarray;
7277 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 2) = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
7278 if (ARGT_ARG(func_args, 2) == 0)
7279 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_CHAR)
7280 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 3) = astb.ptr0c;
7281 else
7282 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 3) = astb.ptr0;
7283 else
7284 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 3) = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 2);
7285 if (ARGT_ARG(func_args, 3) == 0)
7286 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 4) = astb.ptr0;
7287 else
7288 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 4) = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 3);
7289 /* get the name of the library routine */
7290 newsym = sym_mkfunc(mkRteRtnNm(rtlRtn), DT_NONE);
7291 /* get the temp and add the necessary statements */
7292 /* need to put this into a temp */
7293 temp_arr =
7294 mk_result_sptr(func_ast, func_args, subscr, DTY(dtype + 1), lhs, &retval);
7295 if (temp_arr != 0) {
7296 /* add temp_arr as argument */
7297 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = retval;
7298 if (ALLOCG(temp_arr)) {
7299 mk_mem_allocate(mk_id(temp_arr), subscr, arg_gbl.std, ast_from_len);
7300 mk_mem_deallocate(mk_id(temp_arr), arg_gbl.std);
7301 }
7302 tmp_lhs_array = TRUE;
7303 } else {
7304 /* lhs was distributed properly for this intr */
7305 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = lhs;
7306 retval = 0;
7307 }
7308 /* add call to function */
7309 /* make every call ICALL iff call changes the first argument and
7310 * no side effect, this will help optimizer
7311 */
7312 ast = mk_func_node(A_ICALL, mk_id(newsym), nargs, newargt);
7313 A_OPTYPEP(ast, A_OPTYPEG(func_ast));
7314 add_stmt_before(ast, arg_gbl.std);
7315 return retval;
7316}
7317
7318/* reshape(source, shape, [pad, order])
7319 *
7320 * Attempt to optimize reshape by representing the result of the reshape
7321 * as a (Cray) pointer of the source argument. The requirements for this
7322 * optimization are:
7323 * o pad & order are not present
7324 * o the source:
7325 * o + is not pointer
7326 * o + is not assumed-shape array with rank > 1 unless the shape is in the
7327 * first dimension
7328 * o + is contiguous
7329 * o + if character, has constant length
7330 * o + if member, shape is not in the parent
7331 * o the extent of the shape array is constant
7332 */
7333static int
7334_reshape(int func_args, DTYPE dtype, int lhs)
7335{
7336 int retval;
7337 int srcarr, shparr; /* source & shape arguments, resp. */
7338 int sptr;
7339 int i, extnt;
7340 int shpdt, edt;
7341 int arrelem;
7342 int subs, subs_dt, stride;
7343 int ast, ast2, asn;
7344 int subscr[MAXSUBS];
7345 int temp;
7346 int temp_p;
7347 ADSC *ad;
7348 int mult;
7349 int zbase;
7350
7351 retval = 0;
7352 if (XBIT(47, 0x20000000))
7353 return 0;
7354 if (ARGT_ARG(func_args, 2) || ARGT_ARG(func_args, 3))
7355 /* pad and order must not be present */
7356 return 0;
7357 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_CHAR) {
7358 if (DDTG(dtype) == DT_ASSCHAR || DDTG(dtype) == DT_ASSNCHAR ||
7359 DDTG(dtype) == DT_DEFERCHAR || DDTG(dtype) == DT_DEFERNCHAR) {
7360 return 0;
7361 }
7362 }
7363 srcarr = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 0);
7364 sptr = find_array(srcarr, NULL);
7365 if (POINTERG(sptr))
7366 return 0;
7367 if (STYPEG(sptr) != ST_MEMBER && SCG(sptr) == SC_DUMMY && ASSUMSHPG(sptr) &&
7368 rank_of_sym(sptr) > 1) {
7369 int shd;
7370 shd = A_SHAPEG(srcarr);
7371 if (SHD_NDIM(shd) > 1)
7372 return 0;
7373 /*
7374 * is the shape in the first dimension and contiguous?
7375 * will be decided a few lines below by the call to
7376 * contiguous_section()
7377 */
7378 }
7379 /*
7380 * Ignore member reference whose shape is in the parent.
7381 */
7382 if (A_TYPEG(srcarr) == A_MEM && !A_SHAPEG(A_MEMG(srcarr)))
7383 return 0;
7384 /*
7385 * if subscripted, make sure the source is contiguous.
7386 */
7387 if (A_TYPEG(srcarr) == A_SUBSCR && !contiguous_section(srcarr))
7388 return 0;
7389 shparr = ARGT_ARG(func_args, 1);
7390 if (A_TYPEG(shparr) == A_MEM && !A_SHAPEG(A_MEMG(shparr)))
7391 /*
7392 * At this time, ignore if the parent has 'shape'; generating the
7393 * subscripted refs of the shape array is currently relatively simple.
7394 */
7395 return 0;
7396
7397 shpdt = A_DTYPEG(shparr);
7398 extnt = extent_of_shape(A_SHAPEG(shparr), 0);
7399 if (!extnt || !A_ALIASG(extnt))
7400 return 0;
7401 extnt = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(A_ALIASG(extnt)));
7402 edt = DTY(shpdt + 1);
7403 /*
7404 * Someday, it sure would be nice if we could detect that the shape
7405 * array represents an array constructor of 'contant' values.
7406 * But for now, just make the 'shape' adjustable.
7407 *
7408 * Create a adjustable array (Cray) pointer temp. It will by
7409 * marked 'RESHAPED' indicating that it will be representing a
7410 * section of memory that has been reshape and that the address
7411 * will be stored in its 'hidden' the pointer variable.
7412 */
7413 temp = sym_get_array("reshap", "r", DTY(A_DTYPEG(srcarr) + 1), extnt);
7414 SCP(temp, SC_BASED);
7415 RESHAPEDP(temp, 1);
7416 /*
7417 * Create the 'hidden' pointer that will locate the beginning of the
7418 * memory.
7419 */
7420 temp_p = sym_get_ptr(temp);
7421 MIDNUMP(temp, temp_p);
7422 ADJARRP(temp, 1);
7423 SEQP(temp, 1);
7424 /*
7425 * Generate the subscripted references of the shape argument to
7426 * represent the upper bounds of each dimension of the result.
7427 * The bounds will be:
7428 * ( 1:SHAPE(1), 1:SHAPE(2), ... )
7429 * Also, create the bounds temps for the upper bound(s), multiplier(s),
7430 * and 'zbase'
7431 */
7432 /*fprintf(STDERR, "RESHAPE SHP ");dbg_print_ast(shparr,0);*/
7433 arrelem = first_element(shparr);
7434 /*fprintf(STDERR, "RESHAPE SHP1");dbg_print_ast(arrelem,0);*/
7435 subs = ASD_SUBS(A_ASDG(arrelem), 0); /* the first subscript value */
7436 subs_dt = A_DTYPEG(subs);
7437 stride = SHD_STRIDE(A_SHAPEG(shparr), 0);
7438 if (!stride || stride == astb.bnd.one)
7439 stride = mk_cval(1, subs_dt);
7440 else if (A_DTYPEG(stride) != subs_dt) {
7441 stride = mk_convert(stride, subs_dt);
7442 }
7443 ad = AD_DPTR(DTYPEG(temp));
7444 AD_ADJARR(ad) = 1;
7445 i = 0;
7446 while (1) {
7447 AD_LWBD(ad, i) = 0;
7448 AD_LWAST(ad, i) = astb.bnd.one;
7449 if (A_DTYPEG(arrelem) == astb.bnd.dtype)
7450 AD_UPBD(ad, i) = arrelem;
7451 else
7452 AD_UPBD(ad, i) = mk_convert(arrelem, astb.bnd.dtype);
7453 AD_UPAST(ad, i) = mk_bnd_ast();
7454 AD_EXTNTAST(ad, i) = AD_UPAST(ad, i);
7455 if (i == 0) {
7456 AD_MLPYR(ad, i) = astb.bnd.one;
7457 } else {
7458 AD_MLPYR(ad, i) = mk_bnd_ast();
7459 }
7460 i++;
7461 if (i >= extnt)
7462 break;
7463 subs = mk_binop(OP_ADD, subs, stride, subs_dt);
7464 subscr[0] = subs;
7465 arrelem = mk_subscr(A_LOPG(arrelem), subscr, 1, edt);
7466 }
7467 /*
7468 * Generate
7469 * 'hidden pointer' = loc(source)
7470 */
7471 ast = ast_intr(I_LOC, DT_PTR, 1, first_element(srcarr));
7472 ast2 = mk_id(temp_p);
7473 asn = mk_assn_stmt(ast2, ast, DT_PTR);
7474 add_stmt_before(asn, arg_gbl.std);
7475 /*fprintf(STDERR, "RESHAPE LOC");dbg_print_ast(asn,0);*/
7476 /*
7477 * Generate
7478 * the assignments to the upper bound and zbase temps
7479 */
7480 mult = astb.bnd.one;
7481 AD_MLPYR(ad, 0) = mult;
7482 for (i = 0; i < extnt; i++) {
7483 asn = mk_assn_stmt(AD_UPAST(ad, i), AD_UPBD(ad, i), astb.bnd.dtype);
7484 add_stmt_before(asn, arg_gbl.std);
7485 if (i) {
7486 mult = mk_mlpyr_expr(astb.bnd.one, AD_UPAST(ad, i - 1), mult);
7487 asn = mk_assn_stmt(AD_MLPYR(ad, i), mult, astb.bnd.dtype);
7488 add_stmt_before(asn, arg_gbl.std);
7489 }
7490 }
7491 zbase = mk_zbase_expr(ad);
7492 if (A_ALIASG(zbase)) {
7493 AD_ZBASE(ad) = zbase;
7494 } else {
7495 AD_ZBASE(ad) = mk_bnd_ast();
7496 asn = mk_assn_stmt(AD_ZBASE(ad), zbase, astb.bnd.dtype);
7497 add_stmt_before(asn, arg_gbl.std);
7498 }
7499 /*
7500 * Return the temp, expressed as a whole section in each dimension,
7501 * Simply returning 'temp' is not sufficient if we need to build a
7502 * descriptor, such as in
7503 * print *, reshape(yy,[3,4]) !!! need descriptor for reshape
7504 */
7505 retval = mk_id(temp);
7506 retval = convert_subscript_in_expr(retval);
7507 /*fprintf(STDERR, "RESHAPE"); dbg_print_ast(retval,0);*/
7508
7509 return retval;
7510}
